9%20military%20campaign%20in%20Gaza%2C%20which%20have%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20over%2028%2C000%20people%2C%20including%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sale%20more%20of%20than%2020%20Hermes%20900%20medium-altitude%2C%20long-endurance%20(MALE)%20UAVs%20to%20Israel%20%E2%80%93%20first%20reported%20on%20February%202%20by%20Neelam%20Mathews%20for%20the%20well-regarded%20defence-related%20website%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shephardmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fuv-online%2Findia-sends-newly-assembled-male-uavs-to-israel%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EShephard%20Media%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20publicly%20acknowledged%20by%20either%20Tel%20Aviv%20or%20New%20Delhi%20but%20sources%20at%20Adani%2C%20communicating%20off%20the%20record%20as%20they%20are%20not%20authorised%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20media%2C%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20last%20week%20that%20the%20export%20had%20indeed%20taken%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20an%20Indian%20conglomerate%20in%20supplying%20drones%20%E2%80%93%20which%20are%20being%20used%20by%20the%20IDF%20for%20attacks%20in%20densely%20populated%20urban%20areas%20in%20Gaza%20%E2%80%93%20appears%20to%20fly%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20official%20position%20seeking%20an%20immediate%20cease-fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Elbit%20Systems%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Findias-first-pvt-uav-facility-takes-off-at-hyderabad%2Farticleshow%2F67096441.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentered%20into%20a%20joint%20venture%20with%20Adani%20Defence%20and%20Aerospace%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%2049%25%20share%20and%20opened%20a%20%2415-million%20facility%20in%20Hyderabad%20to%20manufacture%20UAVs%20for%20the%20first%20time%20outside%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%20contacted%20the%20Israeli%20defence%20firm%2C%20a%20spokesperson%2C%20Nimrod%20Karmi%2C%20simply%20responded%20that%20they%20could%20%E2%80%9Cconfirm%20that%20Elbit%20Systems%20collaborates%20with%20Adani%2C%20which%20is%20a%20supplier%20to%20our%20UAS%20%5BUnmanned%20Aerial%20Systems%5D%20supply%20chain%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarmi%20added%20that%20Elbit%20Systems%20%E2%80%9Ccannot%20comment%20on%20the%20details%20of%20specific%20contracts%2C%20including%20identifying%20suppliers%20and%20the%20content%20they%20provide%20to%20different%20customers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EShephard%20Media%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20UAVs%20were%20delivered%20with%20fully%20assembled%20carbon%20composite%20aerostructures%20produced%20at%20the%2050%2C000%20sq.%20ft%20Adani%20facility%20in%20Hyderabad.%20The%20report%20also%20indicated%20that%20Elbit%20provided%20Hermes%20900%20kits%20to%20India%2C%20along%20with%20necessary%20tools%20like%20sensors%20and%20engines%2C%20for%20the%20assembly%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202023%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2FHwI0q%23selection-1077.0-1085.1%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EHindu%3C%2Fi%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20based%20on%20insights%20from%20an%20anonymous%20source%20regarding%20the%20delivery%20timeline%20of%20Hermes%20900%20UAVs%20for%20the%20Indian%20defence%20services%20amidst%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20aerostructure%20of%20Hermes%20900%20had%20already%20been%20manufactured%20in%20Hyderabad.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20equipment%20has%20to%20come%20in%20from%20Israel%2C%20which%20has%20already%20arrived.%20So%20there%20is%20no%20impact%20in%20that%20regard%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20source%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fhaaretz-labels%2F2023-02-12%2Fty-article-labels%2F.premium%2Fopening-the-skies-elbit-systems-is-bringing-the-world-of-drones-to-the-civilian-market%2F00000186-44d8-d553-adb6-dedd1c9c0000%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EHaaretz%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%202023%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20UAV%20systems%20in%20the%20Aerospace%20Division%20at%20Elbit%20Systems%2C%20Vered%20Haimovich%2C%20said%20the%20Hermes%20900%20has%20been%20Elbit%20System%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20drone%2C%20which%20has%20been%20operationally%20used%20by%20the%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20since%202015.%20It%20has%20also%20taken%20part%20%E2%80%9Cin%20all%20rounds%20of%20conflict%20in%20recent%20years%E2%80%9D%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrones%2C%20particularly%20the%20Hermes%20900%2C%20play%20a%20pivotal%20role%20for%20Israel%20in%20the%20ongoing%20military%20operations%20in%20Gaza%2C%20initiated%20after%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%202023%20that%20left%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisraeli-military-opens-probe-into-reports-oct-7-friendly-fire-deaths-2024-02-06%2F%5C%22%3E%20over%201%2C200%20dead%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20whom%20were%20civilians%20and%20non-combatants.%20With%20its%20extended%20endurance%20exceeding%2030%20hours%2C%20the%20Hermes%20900%20provides%20crucial%20surveillance%20capabilities%20for%20Israeli%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20a%20correspondent%20from%20the%3Ci%3E%20Telegraph%3C%2Fi%3E%20visited%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Palmachim%20air%20base%20and%20observed%20how%20Israeli%20soldiers%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fworld-news%2F2023%2F12%2F15%2Fat-the-helm-of-israels-lethal-eye-in-the-sky%2F%5C%22%3Eremotely%20operating%20Hermes%20900%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20not%20just%20surveillance%2C%20but%20also%20to%20deliver%20small%20laser-guided%20bombs%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20military%20wing%20of%20Hamas%20last%20month%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.palestinechronicle.com%2Fshooting-down-israeli-drones-resistance-roundup-day-89%2F%5C%22%3Eclaimed%2