C%20reports%20Sacnilk.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFashionable%20Now%20To%20Demolish%20Homes%26quot%3B%3A%20High%20Court%20On%20Ujjain%20Bulldozer%20Action%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20strong%20remarks%20on%20bulldozer%20action%20against%20those%20accused%20in%20criminal%20cases%2C%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20has%20said%20it%20has%20become%20%26quot%3Bfashionable%26quot%3B%20for%20civic%20authorities%20to%20demolish%20homes%20without%20following%20proper%20procedure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indore%20bench%20of%20the%20high%20court%20made%20the%20observations%20earlier%20this%20month%20in%20a%20case%20relating%20to%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20home%20of%20Rahul%20Langri%2C%20who%20faces%20a%20case%20of%20voluntarily%20causing%20hurt%20to%20extort%20property.%20He%20is%20accused%20of%20threatening%20and%20assaulting%20a%20man%2C%20who%20later%20died%20by%20suicide.%20Langri%20was%20arrested%20and%20sent%20to%20jail.%20Police%20then%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20civic%20body%20and%20his%20two-storey%20house%20in%20Ujjain%20was%20razed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELangri's%20wife%20Radha%20approached%20the%20court%20and%20said%20in%20her%20petition%20that%20a%20notice%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Raisa%20Bi%2C%20the%20previous%20owner%2C%20was%20served%20and%20the%20house%20was%20razed%20the%20next%20day%20without%20hearing%20them%20out.%20The%20house%2C%20she%20said%20in%20her%20petition%2C%20was%20not%20illegal.%20She%20said%20the%20house%20was%20registered%20with%20the%20housing%20board%20and%20they%20had%20taken%20a%20bank%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Vivek%20Rusia%20ruled%20that%20the%20demolition%20was%20illegal%20and%20awarded%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20each%20to%20Radha%20Langri%20and%20her%20mother-in-law%20Vimla%20Gurjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20ordered%20action%20against%20civic%20officials%20for%20carrying%20out%20the%20demolition.%20The%20petitioners%20have%20now%20decided%20to%20move%20the%20civil%20court%20for%20higher%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20observed%20repeatedly%20by%20this%20court%2C%20it%20has%20become%20fashionable%20now%20for%20local%20administration%20and%20local%20bodies%20to%20demolish%20any%20house%20by%20drawing%20up%20proceedings%20without%20complying%20with%20the%20principal%20of%20natural%20justice%20and%20publish%20it%20in%20the%20newspaper.%20It%20appears%20that%20in%20this%20case%20also%20the%20criminal%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20one%20of%20the%20family%20members%20of%20the%20petitioners%20and%20demolition%20activities%20were%20carried%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20added%20that%20instead%20of%20razing%20the%20houses%2C%20the%20petitioners%20should%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20get%20the%20construction%20regularised.%20It%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bdemolition%20should%20be%20the%20last%20recourse%20to%20be%20followed%2C%20that%20too%20after%20giving%20a%20proper%20opportunity%20to%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20house%20to%20get%20it%20regularized%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20Radha%20Langri%20alleged%20that%20her%20husband%20was%20jailed%20on%20false%20charges%20and%20their%20house%20demolished.%20%26quot%3BThey%20gave%20a%20day's%20notice%20and%20then%20razed%20our%20home.%20We%20tried%20to%20show%20them%20the%20property%20papers%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20listen.%20Now%20we%20have%20got%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20She%20added%20that%20a%20crime%20is%20committed%20by%20an%20individual%20and%20not%20by%20the%20family.%20%26quot%3BThis%20(bulldozer%20action)%20should%20not%20be%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20counsel%20Tehzeeb%20Khan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20criminal%20stays%20in%20a%20house%2C%20it%20does%20not%20mean%20every%20person%20in%20that%20house%20is%20a%20criminal.%20Razing%20his%20house%20will%20punish%20the%20innocents%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707728700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F1fdobhe8_mp-bulldozer-action-split_625x300_12_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-high-court-fashionable-now-to-demolish-homes-high-court-on-ujjain-bulldozer-action-5042572%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20strong%20remarks%20on%20bulldozer%20action%20against%20those%20accused%20in%20criminal%20cases%2C%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20has%20said%20it%20has%20become%20%26quot%3Bfashionable%26quot%3B%20for%20civic%20authorities%20to%20demolish%20homes%20without%20following%20proper%20procedure.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-high-court-fashionable-now-to-demolish-homes-high-court-on-ujjain-bulldozer-action-5042572%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-high-court-fashionable-now-to-demolish-homes-high-court-on-ujjain-bulldozer-action-5042572%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-high-court-fashionable-now-to-demolish-homes-high-court-on-ujjain-bulldozer-action-5042572%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Berlin%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98In%20the%20Belly%20of%20a%20Tiger%E2%80%99%20Puts%20World%20Cinema%20Icons%20in%20Service%20of%20Indian%20Village%20Tale%2C%20Drops%20Trailer%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707728400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIN-THE-BELLY-OF-A-TIGER-Still-3-cr-res.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235907274%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20director%20and%20cinematographer%20Jatla%20Siddhartha%20has%20assembled%20seve