-of-shares%2Farticleshow%2F107624481.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Sushmita%20Sen%20is%20a%20very%20strong%20woman'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707728091000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107623699%2Cimgsize-27022.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fexclusive-interview-with-sikander-kher-sushmita-sens-strength%2Farticleshow%2F107622934.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107622934.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESikander%20Kher%20discusses%20his%20character%20Daulat%20in%20'Aarya'%20and%20his%20bond%20with%20Sushmita%20Sen.%20He%20reflects%20on%20his%20journey%20with%20the%20show%20and%20praises%20the%20team%20behind%20it%2C%20especially%20Ram%20Madhvani.%20He%20also%20talks%20about%20his%20family's%20review%20of%20'Aarya'%20and%20the%20feedback%20he%20receives%20from%20his%20mother.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Mankermi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Fashionable%20to%20Demolish%20Houses%20Without%20Due%20Procedure%2C%20Should%20Be%20Last%20Recourse%E2%80%99%3A%20MP%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F16172609%2FUntitled-design-2021-07-16T172559.085.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20case%20regarding%20illegal%20demolition%20of%20houses%2C%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20high%20court%20has%20directed%20%E2%80%9Cdisciplinary%20action%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20concerned%20municipal%20authorities%20and%20awarded%20Rs%201%20lakh%20in%20compensation%20to%20the%20petitioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%2C%20Radha%20Langri%2C%20had%20approached%20the%20court%20seeking%20compensation%20for%20the%20demolition%20of%20her%20houses%20carried%20out%20without%20following%20due%20procedure%20by%20the%20Ujjain%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(UMC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Vivek%20Rusia%2C%20while%20delivering%20the%20ruling%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20observed%20repeatedly%20by%20this%20court%2C%20it%20has%20become%20fashionable%20now%20for%20local%20administration%20and%20local%20bodies%20to%20demolish%20any%20house%20by%20drawing%20up%20proceedings%20without%20complying%20with%20the%20Principal%20of%20Natural%20Justice%20and%20publish%20it%20in%20the%20newspaper.%20It%20appears%20that%20in%20this%20case%20also%20the%20criminal%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20one%20of%20the%20family%20members%20of%20the%20petitioners%20and%20demolition%20activities%20were%20carried%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUMC%20argued%20that%20the%20demolitions%20were%20justified%20as%20the%20houses%20(house%20no.%20466%20and%20467)%20had%20been%20constructed%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20Act%20since%20the%20petitioners%20had%20not%20obtained%20building%20permission%20beforehand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20court%20said%20that%20while%20no%20one%20has%20the%20right%20to%20construct%20a%20house%20without%20proper%20permission%2C%20demolition%20should%20be%20considered%20as%20a%20last%20resort.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20should%20only%20be%20carried%20out%20after%20providing%20the%20house%20owner%20with%20a%20fair%20chance%20to%20rectify%20the%20situation%20by%20obtaining%20regularisation%2C%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fhigh-court%2Fmadhya-pradesh-high-court%2Ffashionable-now-to-demolish-houses-without-complying-with-principles-of-natural-justice-demolition-should-be-the-last-recourse-mp-high-court-249130%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmuslims-targeted-in-128-demolitions-617-people-affected-amnesty-reports-on-bulldozer-action%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Muslims%20Targeted%20in%20128%20Demolitions%2C%20617%20People%20Affected%E2%80%99%3A%20Amnesty%20Reports%20on%20Bulldozer%20Action%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20pointed%20out%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20ownership%20details%20of%20the%20houses%20and%20noted%20that%20a%20fabricated%20%3Cem%3Epanchnama%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20been%20prepared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UMC%20alleged%20that%20house%20no.%20466%20was%20owned%20by%20one%20Parvez%20Khan%2C%20not%20Langri%2C%20and%20the%20other%20was%20registered%20under%20one%20Uma.%20However%2C%20the%20court%20found%20that%20no%20one%20by%20the%20name%20of%20Parvez%20Khan%20exists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fhigh-court%2Fmadhya-pradesh-high-court%2Ffashionable-now-to-demolish-houses-without-complying-with-principles-of-natural-justice-demolition-should-be-the-last-recourse-mp-high-court-249130%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CHad%20the%20building%20officer%20gone%20to%20the%20spot%20he%20would%20have%20been%20informed%20about%20the%20name%20of%20the%20petitioner%20about%20the%20ownership.%20There%20is%20no%20such%20person%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Parvez%20Khan%2C%20there%20is%20no%20such%20document%20to%20show%20that%20he%20purchased%20the%20property%20only%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20this%20so%20called%20oral%20information%20the%20panchnama%20was%20drawn%20and%20drastic%20action%20for%20demolition%20has%20been%20taken.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20demolition%20of%20house%20no.%20466%20by%20serving%20a%20notice%20to%20a%20fictitious%20person%20Parvez%20Khan%20is%20a%20highly%20illegal%20and%20arbitrary%20action%20for%20which%20disciplinary%20action%20is%20liable%20to%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20concerned%20officers%20and%20employee%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20house%20no.%20467%2C%20the%20court%20said%20that%20demolition%20notice%20was%20issued%20to%20Uma%20in%20a%20careless%20manner%20and%20without%20any%20acknowledgment.%20The%20bench%20pulled%20up%20the%20corporation%20authorities%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20proper%20procedure%20and%20arbitrary%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20were%20also%20given%20the%20option%20to%20seek%20further%20compensation%20for%20their%20losses%20through%20a%20civil%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBulldozer%20action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20human%20rights%20organisation%20Amnesty%20International%2C%20last%20week%2C%20released%20two%20reports%20titled%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20speak%20up%2C%20your%20house%20will%20be%20demolished%E2%80%99%3A%20Bulldozer%20Injustice%20in%20India%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Unearthing%20Accountability%3A%20JCB%E2%80%99s%20Role%20and%20Responsibility%20in%20Bulldozer%20Injustice%20in%20India%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%20document%20the%20punitive%20demolition%20of%20Muslim%20properties%20in%20at%20least%20five%20states%20using%20JCB-branded%20bulldozers%20calling%20it%20%E2%80%9Ca%20hate%20campaign%20against%20the%20minority%20community%E2%80%9D.%20According%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20demolitions%2C%20often%20enacted%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20removing%20illegal%20construction%2C%20violated%20due%20process%20outlined%20in%20domestic%20and%20international%20human%20rights%20law.%20They%20also%20highlighted%20that%20Muslim-concentrated%20localities%20were%20targeted%2C%20while%20Muslim-owned%20properties%20were%20selectively%20demolished%2C%20leaving%20nearby%20Hindu-owned%20properties%20untouched.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707727824000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F16172609%2FUntitled-design-2021-07-16T172559.085.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffashionable-to-demolish-house