ws%2Fdrake-wins-234-million-betting-on-kansas-city-chiefs-cant-bet-against-the-swifties%2Farticleshow%2F107621679.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107621679.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERapper%20Drake%20won%20%242.3%20million%20from%20a%20%241.15%20million%20bet%20on%20the%20Kansas%20City%20Chiefs%20in%20the%202024%20Super%20Bowl.%20He%20credited%20Taylor%20Swift%20and%20her%20fanbase%2C%20the%20Swifties%2C%20for%20his%20confidence.%20High-stakes%20gambling%20is%20not%20unfamiliar%20territory%20for%20Drake%2C%20who%20previously%20lost%20%242%20million%20over%20a%20UFC%20fight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Teacher%20Took%20Student%20Into%20A%20Locked%20Bathroom%2C%20Later%20Handed%20Him%20Money%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20ex-prodigy%20from%20the%20Bronx%20High%20School%20of%20Science%2C%20who%20later%20became%20a%20chemistry%20teacher%20in%20the%20city%2C%20resigned%20last%20year%20following%20an%20investigation%20that%20revealed%20her%20involvement%20in%20an%20inappropriate%20relationship%20with%20a%20male%20student%20at%20the%20Manhattan%20high%20school%20where%20she%20was%20employed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShoshana%20Leffler%2C%20aged%2037%2C%20was%20once%20a%20star%20student%20at%20Bronx%20High%20School%20alongside%20her%20twin%20brother%20Abba%2C%20both%20recognized%20among%20300%20semifinalists%20in%20the%20prestigious%20Intel%20Science%20Talent%20Search.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20her%20education%20at%20Princeton%20and%20NYU%2C%20she%20secured%20a%20teaching%20position%20in%202019%20with%20the%20city%20Department%20of%20Education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20February%202023%2C%20Leffler%2C%20then%2036%20years%20old%2C%20was%20captured%20on%20video%20escorting%20a%2017-year-old%20male%20student%20into%20a%20locked%20bathroom%20at%20the%20High%20School%20for%20Health%20Careers%20and%20Sciences%20in%20Manhattan's%20Fort%20George.%20She%20was%20later%20seen%20giving%20the%20teenager%20a%20sum%20of%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20occurred%20in%20the%20bathroom%20can%20only%20be%20speculated%20about%20since%20Leffler%20resigned%20from%20the%20DOE%20without%20providing%20an%20explanation%2C%26quot%3B%20Anastasia%20Coleman%2C%20the%20Special%20Commissioner%20of%20Investigation%20for%20city%20schools%2C%20said%20in%20a%20report%20obtained%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F02%2F10%2Fmetro%2Fnyc-teacher-had-inappropriate-relationship-with-male-student%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20surveillance%20camera%20captured%20Leffler%20and%20the%20unnamed%20student%20%26quot%3Bengaging%20in%20conversation%26quot%3B%20at%2010%3A35%20am%20on%20a%20Tuesday%20morning%20-%20one%20minute%20into%20the%20fourth%20period%2C%20when%20the%20teen%20%26quot%3Bshould%20have%20been%20in%20class%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20SCI%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20outlet%20reported%20that%20an%20assistant%20principal%20spotted%20the%20two%20and%20rebuked%20Leffler%20for%20the%20improper%20tete-a-tete.%20But%20Leffler%20did%20not%20end%20the%20conversation%20there%2C%20she%20took%20the%20boy%20to%20the%20building's%20fifth%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%2C%20they%20%26quot%3Bsought%20out%20a%20private%20room%20where%20security%20cameras%20could%20not%20record%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20investigators%20concluded%20-%20a%20staff%20bathroom%20with%20a%20lockable%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20in%20the%20washroom%20for%207%20minutes.%20It%20was%20interrupted%20after%20another%20staff%20member%20arrived%20to%20use%20the%20facilities%20and%20found%20the%20bathroom%20locked.%20Once%20the%20staff%20member%20left%2C%20Leffler%20and%20the%20teen%20were%20filmed%20leaving%20separately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20Mr%20Leffler%20met%20up%20with%20the%20student%20in%20the%20stairwell%20again%2C%20where%20she%20was%20seen%20%26quot%3Bhanding%20%5Bhim%5D%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20money%2C%20him%20pocketing%20this%20money%2C%20and%20then%20leaving%20the%20stairwell%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20investigators%20found%20no%20evidence%20of%20contact%20between%20Leffler%20and%20the%20boy%20in%20the%20teacher's%20phone%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20student%20would%20not%20testify%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20media%20outlet%20reported.%20Leffler%20quit%20while%20the%20probe%20was%20ongoing%2C%20and%20later%20refused%20to%20be%20questioned%2C%20leaving%20the%20nature%20of%20their%20relationship%20a%20mystery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707727380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Frs6c9au_shoshana-leffler_625x300_12_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchemistry-teacher-in-us-took-student-into-a-locked-bathroom-later-handed-him-money-probe-5042329%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shoshana%20Leffler%2C%20aged%2037%2C%20was%20once%20a%20star%20student%20at%20Bronx%20High%20School%20alongside%20her%20twin%20brother%20Abba%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchemistry-teacher-in-us-took-student-into-a-locked-bathroom-later-handed-him-money-probe-5042329%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchemistry-teacher-in-us-took-student-into-a-locked-bathroom-later-handed-him-money-probe-5042329%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchemistry-teacher-in-us-took-student-into-a-locked-bathroom-later-handed-him-money-probe-5042329%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Times%20Kangana%20Gave%20Style%20Go