20asked%20if%20Mr%20Chavan%20is%20joining%20the%20party.%20%26quot%3BI%20heard%20about%20Ashok%20Chavan%20from%20media.%20But%20only%20thing%20I%20can%20say%20now%20is%20that%20several%20good%20leaders%20from%20Congress%20are%20in%20touch%20of%20BJP.%20Those%20leaders%20who%20are%20connected%20with%20the%20masses%20are%20feeling%20suffocated%20in%20Congress.%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20some%20big%20faces%20will%20join%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20then%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Congress%20sources%2C%20Mr%20Chavan's%20differences%20with%20state%20party%20chief%20Nana%20Patole%20on%20selection%20of%20candidates%20may%20have%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20his%20decision%20to%20switch%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESon%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Shankarrao%20Chavan%2C%20Ashok%20Chavan%20wields%20significant%20influence%20in%20the%20Nanded%20region%20and%20this%20switch%20may%20hurt%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20upcoming%20polls.%20This%20also%20plays%20out%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20tall%20poll%20challenge%20facing%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20--%20comprising%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20camp%20of%20NCP%20and%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshok%20Chavan%20has%20had%20an%20eventful%20political%20journey%20so%20far.%20Starting%20out%20as%20a%20student%20leader%20during%20his%20college%20days%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20hold%20key%20posts%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20including%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20chief%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee.%20He%20has%20served%20as%20an%20MP%20from%20Nanded%20on%20two%20occasions%20and%20been%20a%20member%20of%20both%20Houses%20of%20the%20state%20legislature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20serving%20as%20state%20minister%2C%20he%20was%20chosen%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%20after%20Vilasrao%20Deshmukh%20stepped%20down%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%202008%20terror%20attacks