20priority%20project.He%20teams%20up%20with%20Ghajini%20director%20A%20R%20Murgadoss%20for%20this%20global%20actioner%2C%20which%20is%20pegged%20at%20the%20budget%20of%20Rs%20400%20crore.%20His%20previous%20release%2C%20Tiger%203%2C%20did%20not%20perform%20well%20at%20the%20box%20office.%20Another%20film%20titled%20'The%20Bull'%20has%20been%20put%20on%20hold.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Do%20Trinamool%20Congress's%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Nominations%20Say%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12124835%2FUntitled-design-9-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWest%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20party%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%2C%20on%20Sunday%2C%20named%20four%20Rajya%20Sabha%20nominees%20of%20the%20party%20for%20the%20coming%20February%2027%20election%2C%20a%20list%20that%20reflected%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20national%2C%20regional%20and%20local%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFive%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seats%20from%20West%20Bengal%20are%20falling%20vacant%20and%20the%20victory%20of%20the%20TMC%20is%20certain%20in%20four%20while%20the%20other%20is%20set%20to%20go%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%20on%20the%20same%20day%20named%20state%20unit%20veteran%20Samik%20Bhattacharya%2C%20a%20former%20MLA%20and%20the%20state%20unit%E2%80%99s%20chief%20spokesperson%2C%20as%20its%20nominee.%20This%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20gesture%20to%20BJP%20%E2%80%98old-timers%E2%80%99%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20have%20recently%20been%20offended%20or%20upset%20by%20the%20growing%20influence%20of%20%E2%80%98newcomers%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20state%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20surprise%20inclusion%20in%20the%20TMC%20list%20was%20senior%20Delhi-based%20journalist%20Sagarika%20Ghose%2C%20while%20senior%20Assam%20leader%20Sushmita%20Dev%20is%20being%20sent%20to%20the%20Upper%20House%20again%2C%20after%20a%20brief%20break%20of%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20two%20other%20TMC%20nominees%20are%20Mamata%20Thakur%2C%20a%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20prominent%20leader%20of%20the%20refugee%20Matua%20community%2C%20and%20Mohammed%20Nadimul%20Haque%2C%20the%20owner%20and%20editor%20of%20Akhbar-e-Mashriq%2C%20one%20of%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20most%20influential%20Urdu%20dailies.%20Haque%2C%20who%20was%20first%20sent%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202012%2C%20got%20a%20straight%20third%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CToday%E2%80%99s%20list%20of%20candidates%20has%20two%20very%20important%20messages.%20Three%20out%20of%20the%20four%20are%20women.%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20sending%20more%20women%20to%20the%20parliament.%20We%20do%20not%20know%20when%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20law%20passed%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20will%20be%20implemented%20but%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20walking%20the%20talk%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dev%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20after%20the%20announcement%20a%20day%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20TMC%20currently%20has%20Dola%20Sen%20and%20Mausam%20Noor%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20the%20inclusion%20of%20three%20more%20would%20mean%20five%20out%20of%2013%20TMC%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20are%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20other%20message%20was%2C%20Dev%20said%20regarding%20her%20nomination%2C%20that%20this%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20politician%20from%20the%20northeast%20has%20been%20twice%20sent%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20from%20outside%20the%20northeast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESagarika%20Ghose%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20TMC%20veterans%2C%20the%20nomination%20of%20Ghose%20reflects%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20ambition%20to%20have%20prominent%20%E2%80%98liberal%20faces%E2%80%99%20addressing%20the%20national%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20Rajya%20Sabha%20team%20already%20includes%20Jawhar%20Sircar%2C%20former%20Prasar%20Bharati%20CEO%20and%20India%20culture%20secretary%2C%20and%20Delhi-based%20journalist-turned-Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20activist%20Saket%20Gokhale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EGhose%2C%20who%20has%20played%20leading%20roles%20both%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20print%20and%20broadcast%20media%2C%20has%20authored%2C%20among%20other%20books%2C%20%3Cem%3EWhy%20I%20Am%20A%20Liberal.%20A%20Manifesto%20for%20Indians%20Who%20Believe%20In%20Individual%20Freedom%3C%2Fem%3E.%20She%20is%20married%20to%20prominent%20TV%20anchor%20Rajdeep%20Sardesai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHer%20foray%20into%20politics%20has%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20to%20many.%20Following%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20announcement%2C%20two%20of%20her%20tweets%20from%20March%2013%2C%202018%2C%20went%20viral%2C%20thanks%20mainly%20to%20her%20detractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20the%20tweets%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsagarikaghose%2Fstatus%2F973491364397756417%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsagarikaghose%2Fstatus%2F973491364397756417%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707792784941000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1zv3Jy9slkaYic3UZYkgyf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20never%20accept%20any%20RS%20ticket%20or%20PS%20ticket%20or%20CS%20ticket%20from%20any%20political%20party%2C%20sir.%20That%20I%20can%20give%20you%20in%20writing%20and%20you%20can%20save%20this%20tweet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(ma