ate%20her%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFormer%20Assam%20Congress%20president%20Ripun%20Bora%20heads%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20Assam%20unit%2C%20while%20Dev%20is%20another%20prominent%20leader.%20The%20party%20had%20asked%20from%20the%20Congress%20four%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%2014%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20%E2%80%93%20Karimganj%2C%20Kokrajhar%2C%20Lakhimpur%2C%20and%20Dhubri%20%E2%80%93%20for%20an%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ENow%20that%20the%20seat-sharing%20talks%20have%20failed%2C%20the%20TMC%20may%20contest%20in%20one%20or%20two%20more%20seats%2C%20like%20Naogaon%2C%20which%20has%20a%20sitting%20Congress%20MP%20but%20the%20TMC%20claims%20to%20have%20good%20organisational%20strength.%20The%20TMC%20has%20never%20won%20any%20assembly%20or%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ll%20sit%20with%20national%20general%20secretary%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20in%20a%20few%20days%20and%20decide%20on%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20we%20are%20going%20to%20contest%20in%20Assam%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dev%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMamata%20Thakur%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMamata%20Thakur%E2%80%99s%20nomination%20assumes%20significance%2C%20coming%2C%20coincidentally%20or%20not%2C%20exactly%20a%20day%20after%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20would%20be%20implemented%20across%20the%20country%20before%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20Notably%2C%20the%20current%20extension%20on%20framing%20Rules%20for%20the%20CAA%20ends%20on%20March%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fheres-why-the-bjp-brings-up-the-caa-but-stops-short-of-implementing-it-in-bengal%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20Why%20the%20BJP%20Brings%20up%20the%20CAA%20%E2%80%93%20But%20Stops%20Short%20of%20Implementing%20it%20%E2%80%93%20in%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThakur%20heads%20one%20section%20of%20Matua%20Mahasangha%2C%20the%20most%20influential%20religious%20body%20of%20the%20Matua-Namasudra%20community%20that%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20strongest%20votaries%20of%20the%20CAA%2C%20which%20grants%20citizenship%20to%20non-Muslims%20who%20have%20migrated%20from%20Muslim-majority%20neighbouring%20countries.%20The%20Matua-Namasudra%20community%20members%20have%20migrated%20from%20Bangladesh%20over%20the%20past%20several%20decades%2C%20many%20of%20them%20in%20the%20face%20of%20persecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20TMC%20has%20vowed%20to%20prevent%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA%20and%20Thakur%20has%20the%20herculean%20task%20of%20convicting%20the%20Matua-Namashudra%20community%20that%20the%20CAA%20would%20not%20be%20beneficial%20for%20them.%20The%20community%20plays%20the%20determining%20factor%20in%20at%20least%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20Bongaon%20and%20Ranaghat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThakur%20was%20earlier%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Bongaon%20but%20lost%20the%202019%20election%20to%20her%20nephew%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Shantanu%20Thakur%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20other%20faction%20of%20the%20Matua%20Mahasangha%20and%20is%20currently%20the%20junior%20shipping%20minister.%20Santanu%20Thakur%20had%20promised%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EVeterans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20other%20TMC%20Rajya%20Sabha%20members%20are%20party%20veterans%20Subrata%20Bakshi%2C%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%2C%20and%20Sukhendu%20Sekhar%20Roy%2C%20north%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20leader%20Prakash%20Chik%20Baraik%20and%20social%20activist%20Samirul%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Rajya%20Sabha%20choice%2C%20Bhattacharya%2C%20has%20been%20a%20prominent%20face%20of%20the%20party%20since%20the%201990s.%20In%202014%2C%20he%20became%20the%20first%20BJP%20MLA%20in%20the%20state%20winning%20on%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20own%20strength.%20However%2C%20he%20lost%20in%20the%202016%20assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CSending%20him%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20is%20a%20message%20to%20all%20veterans%20to%20have%20patience%20and%20faith%20on%20Modi-Shah%E2%80%99s%20leadership.%20Those%20who%20remain%20dedicated%20and%20disciplined%20will%20be%20rewarded%20on%20time.%20Bhattacharya%20remained%20quite%20cornered%20for%20much%20of%20the%20past%20few%20years%20but%20he%20never%20breached%20party%20discipline%20or%20became%20aloof%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20BJP%20state%20unit%20leader%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBJP%20currently%20has%20one%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20from%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Ananta%20Rai%2C%20who%20represents%20the%20Rajbanshi%20community%20of%20Cooch%20Behar%20and%20neighbouring%20districts%20in%20northern%20West%20Bengal%20but%20currently%20lives%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707726654000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12124835%2FUntitled-design-9-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftmc-rajya-sabha-sagarika-ghose-mamata-sushmita-dev%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20BJP%20named%20a%20Bengal%20unit%20veteran%20in%20an%20apparent%20move%20to%20assure%20old-timers%2C%20the%20choices%20made%20by%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20party%20were%20interesting.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftmc-rajya-sabha-sagarika-ghose-mamata-sushmita-dev%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Family%20Animation%20%E2%80%98Ploey%202%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Legend%20of%20the%20Winds%E2%80%99%20to%20Launch%20into%20International%20Markets%20With%20The%20Playmaker%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707726600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPLOEY-2.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235906705%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Playmaker%20has%20signed%20with%20GunHil%20to%20handle%20the%20world%20sales%20for%20%E2%80%9CPloey%202%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Legend%20of%20the%20Winds%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20is%20described%20as%20%E2%80%9Can%20endearing%20and%20funny%20road%20movie%20for%20the%20whole%20family%20about%20pursuing%20your%20own%20ideals%20to%20serve%20the%20greater%20good.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Playmaker%20will%20present%20the%20film%20at%20the%20European%20Film%20Market%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Leo%20Barraclough%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fploey-2-the-legend-of-the-winds-the-playmaker-1235906705%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fploey-2-the-legend-of-the-winds-the-playmaker-1235906705%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fploey-2-the-legend-of-the-winds-the-playmaker-1235906705%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%3A%20Sub-Grouping%20SCs%20%7C%20Prioritise-Not%20'Prefer'-Treating%20More%20Injured%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EConsider%20a%20hypothetical%20situation.%20You%20come%20across%20two%20injured%20and%20parched%20people.%20One%20is%20more%20severely%20injured%20than%20the%20other.%20You%20have%20a%20small%20bottle%20of%20water%20that%20will%20only%20suffice%20for%20one.%20Who%20will%20you%20give%20this%20water%20to%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20physical%20injuries%20such%20as%20bruises%2C%20lacerations%20and%20burns%2C%20injuries%20caused%20by%20discrimination%20may%20not%20be%20visible%20to%20the%20naked%20eye.%20It%20is%20hard%20to%20figure%20out%20who%20is%20injured%2C%20and%20in%20what%20ways.%20Among%20other%20things%2C%20empirical%20exercises%20such%20as%20censuses%20are%20helpful%20in%20viewing%20the%20aggregate%20effects%20of%20discrimination.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaste-wise-population-census-not-enumerated-since-independence-minister-3622924%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOn%2520being%2520asked%2520the%2520details%2Cpublished%2520from%2520a%2520syndicated%2520feed.)%5C%22%3Ecensus%20of%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%20remains%20suspended%2C%20and%20the%20need%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20is%20selectively%20realised%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-caste-based-survey-ndtv-explains-4443519%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20state%20of%20Bihar%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Yet%2C%20statistical%20information%20is%20not%20the%20sole%20basis%20for%20state%20action.%20The%20executive%2C%20the%20legislature%20and%20the%20judiciary%20are%20frequently%20called%20upon%20to%20make%20decisions%20on%20matters%20of%20reservation%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20affirmative%20action.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EReservations%20Are%20Not%20'Exceptions'%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudges%20have%20long%20delved%20into%20the%20doctrinal%20justifications%20for%20caste-based%20reservations%20since%20early%20days%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EState%20of%20Madras%20v.%20Champakam%20Dorairajan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1951).%20These%20justifications%20have%20invoked%20constitutional%20ideas%20of%20a%20welfare%20state%2C%20equality%2C%20non-discrimination%2C%20equal%20opportunity%2C%20and%20adequate%20representation.%20Non-discrimination%20has%20been%20often%20invoked%20in%20opposition%20to%20reservations.%20In%20a%20paradox%20of%20sorts%2C%20this%20opposition%20views%20all%20caste-based%20reservations%20as%20fundamentally%20discriminatory.%20At%20the%20very%20best%2C%20begrudgingly%20or%20graciously%2C%20as%20a%20charitable%20concession%20perhaps%2C%20this%20opposition%20accepts%20reservations%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bexception%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20principle%20of%20equality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20has%20taken%20an%20exceptionally%20large%20bench%20of%20nine%20Supreme%20Court%20judges%20in%3Cem%3E%20Indra%20Sawhney%20%26amp%3B%20Others%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1992)%2C%20to%20clarify%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Freservations%5C%22%3Ereservations%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20not%20exceptions%20but%20provisions%20of%20equality.%20The%20doctrinal%20understanding%20of%20affirmative%20action%20in%20the%20US%20has%20taken%20similarly%20dialectical%20positions.%20The%20more%20avid%20supporters%20of%20affirmative%20action%20characterise%20it%20as%20a%20remedy%20against%20discrimination%3B%20other%20supporters%20characterise%20it%20as%20an%20exception%20to%20the%20anti-discrimination%20doctrine%2C%20while%20the%20opposition%20characterise%20affirmative%20action%20as%20an%20unjustifiable%20%26quot%3Bpreferential%20treatment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20impugned%20legislation%20currently%20pending%20adjudication%20appears%20to%20have%20lapsed%20into%20the%20framework%20of%20preference.%20Section%204(5)%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstates-cant-be-selective-in-granting-quota-to-backward-classes-supreme-court-5020583%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Chinnaiah%2520judgment%2520had%2520held%2CArticle%2520341%2520of%2520the%2520Constitution.%5C%22%3EPunjab%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Backward%20Classes%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Reservation%20in%20Services)%20Act%2C%202006%20provides%20%26quot%3Ba%20first%20preference%26quot%3B%20to%20Balmikis%20and%20Mazhabi%20Sikhs%20in%2050%25%20of%20the%20quota%20reserved%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC).%20A%20five-judge%20constitution%20bench%20in%20%3Cem%3EE.V.%20Chinnaiah%20v%20State%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2004)%20had%20disallowed%20such%20subclassification%20because%20it%20was%20considered%20manipulation%20of%20the%20originally%20notified%20list%20of%20the%20SC.%20Now%2C%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20impugned%20provision%20hangs%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20larger%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-scs-sts-may-not-be-homogenous-supreme-court-on-sub-classification-5013359%5C%22%3Eseven-judge%20constitutional%20bench%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20'Creamy%20Layer'%20Debate%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20'preference'%20has%20invoked%20corresponding%20ideas%20of%20preferential%20treatment%20that%20are%20inimical%20to%20the%20doctrinal%20foundations%20of%20reservations.%20It%20invokes%20the%20same%20dialectical%20positions%20previously%20raised%20between%20the%20reserved%20categories%20of%20the%20SC%20and%20the%20unreserved%20General%20categories.%20Only%20now%20must%20the%20so-called%20preferential%20treatment%20be%20justified%20within%20the%20SC%20categories%2C%20setting%20intense%20intra-group%20rivalries%20among%20the%20SCs.%20Troubling%20questions%20arise%20over%20who%20is%20more%20discriminated%20against%2C%20more%20dehumanised%2C%20subordinated%2C%20marginalised%2C%20disadvantaged%2C%20oppressed%2C%20silenced%2C%20erased%2C%20and%20victimised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20opens%20the%20Pandora's%20box%20of%20%26quot%3Bcreamy%20layer%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20juridical%20invention%20of%20Indra%20Sawhney%20(1992)%20that%20sought%20to%20distinguish%20a%20relatively%20better-off%20segment%20among%20the%20Backward%20Classes%20(BC)%20from%20the%20actual%20backward%20classes-leading%20to%20wide%20intra-group%20resentment%20and%20contestations.%20Similarly%20divisive%20sentiments%20are%20now%20being%20raised%20among%20anti-caste%20Dalit%20groups.%20Some%20SC%20groups%20invoke%20their%20experiences%20of%20caste-based%20%26quot%3Buntouchability%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20distinguishing%20factor%20from%20the%20BC%2C%20thereby%20rendering%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20creamy%20layer%20inapplicable%20to%20the%20SC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Justice%20Gavai%20has%20pointed%20to%20internal%20hierarchies%20and%20historical%20practices%20of%20%26quot%3Buntouchability%26quot%3B%20among%20the%20SC%20groups.%20He%20reportedly%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWere%20they%20(scavengers)%20not%20untouchables%20amongst%20the%20untouchables%3F%26quot%3B%20This%20slippery%20slope%20will%20raise%20more%20questions%20about%20the%20caste-specificity%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%201989%2C%20such%20that%20the%20SC%20persons%20cannot%20be%20perpetrators%20of%20offences%20(under%20Section%203%20thereof)%20against%20other%20SC%20persons.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EOn%20Substantive%20Equality%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20conundrum%20is%2C%20inadvertently%20and%20partly%2C%20an%20offshoot%20of%20the%20preferential%20treatment%20discourse.%20In%20the%20first%20instance%2C%20it%20could%20have%20been%20avoided%20by%20substituting%20the%20word%20'preference'%20with%20priority%20in%20the%20Punjab%20Act.%20It%20would%20only%20be%20a%20minor%20discursive%20strategy%2C%20a%20sidestepping%20of%20sorts.%20It%20would%20not%20make%20a%20substantial%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Chief%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20has%20obliquely%20hinted%2C%20the%20existing%20jurisprudence%20on%20substantive%20equality%20in%20India%20is%20robust%20enough%20to%20uphold%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20sub-classification%20of%20SC%20groups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20to%20answer%20the%20hypothetical%20question%20at%20the%20start%20of%20this%20opinion%2C%20if%20I%20were%20a%20functionary%20of%20the%20state%2C%20I%20would%20give%20respite%20to%20the%20one%20who%20is%20more%20severely%20injured.%20I%20would%20do%20this%20as%20a%20reasoned%20prioritising%20(of%20scarce%20resources)%2C%20not%20as%20a%20whimsical%20preference%20of%20one%20subordinate%20group%20over%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E(Prof.%20Dr.%20Sumit%20Baudh%20(they%2F%20he)%20teaches%20constitutional%20law.%20Views%20in%20this%20opinion%20are%20informed%20by%20their%20comparative%20understanding%20of%20Critical%20Race%20Theory.%20He%20can%20be%20reached%20on%20X%20%40BaudhSumit)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707726540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fe8bgk2vo_supreme-court-getty_625x300_31_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-supreme-court-sub-classifying-scs-scheduled-castes-lets-prioritise-not-prefer-treating-the-more-injured-first-5041896%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20than%20just%20a%20whimsical%20preferential%20treatment%20of%20one%20group%20over%20the%20other%2C%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20debate%20is%20the%20question%20of%20which%20are%20the%20more%20injured%20groups%20that%20the%20state%20needs%20to%20prioritise%20for%20affirmative%20action.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-supreme-court-sub-classifying-scs-scheduled-castes-lets-prioritise-not-prefer-treating-the-more-injured-first-5041896%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-supreme-court-sub-classifying-scs-scheduled-castes-lets-prioritise-not-prefer-treating-the-more-injured-first-5041896%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-supreme-court-sub-classifying-scs-scheduled-castes-lets-prioritise-not-prefer-treating-the-more-injured-first-5041896%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20rescues%20two%20hostages%20in%20Rafah%20amid%20deadly%20strikes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707726346000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%