years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20had%20on%20January%2023%20asked%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20appeals%20filed%20by%20the%20four%20convicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoumya%20Vishwanathan%2C%20who%20worked%20with%20a%20leading%20English%20news%20channel%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20September%2030%2C%202008%2C%20on%20Nelson%20Mandela%20Marg%20in%20south%20Delhi%20while%20she%20was%20returning%20home%20from%20work%20in%20her%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20special%20court%20had%20on%20November%2026%2C%202023%2C%20awarded%20two%20life%20terms%20to%20Ravi%20Kapoor%2C%20Amit%20Shukla%2C%20Baljeet%20Malik%20and%20Ajay%20Kumar%20under%20Section%20302%20(murder)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20and%20Section%203(1)(i)%20(committing%20organised%20crime%20resulting%20in%20the%20death%20of%20any%20person)%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20Control%20of%20Organised%20Crime%20Act%20(MCOCA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20sentences%20will%20run%20%26quot%3Bconsecutively%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fifth%20convict%2C%20Ajay%20Sethi%2C%20was%20handed%20down%20three%20years%20of%20simple%20imprisonment%20under%20section%20411%20(dishonestly%20receiving%20stolen%20property)%20of%20the%20IPC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%2C%20however%2C%20set%20off%20the%20three-year%20sentence%20against%20the%20time%20Sethi%20had%20already%20served%2C%20noting%20he%20remained%20in%20custody%20for%20more%20than%2014%20years%20and%20underwent%20incarceration%20during%20the%20trial%20for%20offences%20under%20the%20IPC%20and%20MCOCA%20for%20conspiring%20to%20abet%2C%20aid%2C%20or%20knowingly%20facilitate%20organised%20crime%20and%20receiving%20proceeds%20of%20organised%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapoor's%20counsel%20had%20submitted%20that%20he%20has%20been%20in%20custody%20for%20the%20last%2014%20years%20and%20nine%20months%20and%20urged%20the%20court%20to%20suspend%20his%20sentence%20during%20the%20pendency%20of%20the%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20prayer%20for%20suspension%20of%20sentence%20was%20also%20made%20by%20advocate%20Amit%20Kumar%2C%20who%20represented%20Shukla%2C%20Malik%20and%20Ajay%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20sentencing%20Kapoor%2C%20Shukla%2C%20Malik%20and%20Kumar%20to%20double%20life%20imprisonment%2C%20the%20trial%20court%20had%20also%20imposed%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%20on%20each%20of%20them.%20It%20had%20imposed%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%207.25%20lakh%20on%20Sethi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20high%20court%20denied%20parole%20to%20Kapoor%2C%20considering%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20offences%20committed%20by%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20four%20convicts%2C%20Kapoor%2C%20Shukla%20and%20Malik%20were%20also%20convicted%20of%20killing%20IT%20professional%20Jigisha%20Ghosh.%20The%20trio%20later%20confessed%20to%20police%20they%20were%20also%20behind%20Vishwanathan's%20murder%2C%20and%20the%20weapon%20used%20for%20killing%20her%20was%20recovered%20from%20their%20possession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20had%20said%20the%20motive%20behind%20Vishwanathan's%20killing%20was%20robbery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20court%20had%20awarded%20the%20death%20penalty%20to%20Kapoor%20and%20Shukla%20and%20sentenced%20Malik%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20in%20the%202009%20Jigisha%20Ghosh%20murder%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20death%20sentence%20was%20commuted%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20by%20the%20high%20court.%20The%20high%20court%20upheld%20Malik's%20life%20sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20prosecution%2C%20Kapoor%20shot%20Vishwanathan%20with%20a%20country-made%20pistol%20while%20chasing%20her%20car%20to%20rob%20her.%20Shukla%2C%20Kumar%20and%20Malik%20were%20also%20with%20Kapoor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20recovered%20the%20car%20used%20in%20the%20murder%20from%20Sethi%20alias%20Chacha.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707723000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22