07621175.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Large%20Gatherings%20Banned%20In%20Delhi%20Till%20March%2012%20Before%20Farmers'%20Mega%20March%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELarge%20gatherings%20have%20been%20banned%20across%20Delhi%20for%20a%20month%20-%20till%20March%2012%20-%20ahead%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Ffarmers-protest%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emega%20protest%20by%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%20starting%20Tuesday.%20Over%20200%20farmer%20unions%20-%20around%2020%2C000%20farmers%20in%20all%20-%20are%20expected%20to%20converge%20on%20the%20national%20capital%20in%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20in%20a%20potential%20replay%20of%20the%20violent%20protests%20in%202020%2F21%20over%20%26quot%3Bblack%26quot%3B%20farm%20laws%20passed%20(and%20then%20scrapped)%20by%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIdentical%20orders%20have%20been%20in%20force%20in%20the%20northeast%20districts%20since%20Saturday%20-%20after%20farmers%2C%20who%20are%20expected%20to%20roll%20in%20200%20tractors%20-%20from%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Punjab%20launched%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%20have%20multiple%20demands%2C%20including%20enactment%20of%20a%20law%20to%20guarantee%20minimum%20support%20price%2C%20or%20MSP%2C%20for%20their%20crops.%20Legal%20assurances%20for%20the%20MSP%20scheme%20was%20part%20of%20the%20protests%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20which%20were%20called%20off%20after%20the%20government%20reached%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20agitating%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20demands%20are%20implementation%20of%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission's%20recommendations%2C%20pensions%20for%20farmers%20and%20farm%20labourers%2C%20waiving%20of%20farm%20debts%2C%20and%20withdrawal%20of%20police%20cases%20filed%20during%20the%202020%2F21%20protests.%20The%20farmers%20also%20want%20justice%20for%20those%20killed%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%3B%20eight%20people%2C%20including%20four%20farmers%2C%20were%20mowed%20down%20by%20cars%20during%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20banning%20gatherings%20-%20under%20Section%20144%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20-%20issued%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20Commissioner%20Sanjay%20Arora%20this%20morning%20also%20bans%20entry%20of%20tractors%20into%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20and%20there%20is%20a%20complete%20ban%20on%20carrying%20of%20guns%20and%20inflammable%20substances%2C%20as%20well%20as%20makeshift%20weapons%20like%20bricks%20and%20stones%2C%20and%20the%20collection%20of%20petrol%20cans.%20Loudspeakers%20are%20also%20banned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyone%20found%20violating%20these%20orders%20will%20be%20arrested%20on%20sight%2C%20the%20police%20have%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20farmers'%20protest%20-%20the%20'Delhi%20Chalo'%20campaign%20organised%20by%20the%20Kisan%20Morcha%20-%20security%20has%20been%20intensified%20along%20the%20Singhu%2C%20Ghazipur%2C%20and%20Tikri%20border%20crossings%20into%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-braces-for-farmers-protest-tomorrow-key-points-5041795%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhy%20Farmers%20Are%20Marching%20To%20Delhi%20Tomorrow%3A%20Key%20Points%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20worrying%20repeat%20of%20police's%20anti-protest%20measures%20from%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20massive%20concrete%20blocks%20have%20been%20lifted%20into%20place%20along%20major%20roads%2C%20to%20block%20the%20marching%20farmers.%20In%202020%2F21%2C%20the%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20and%20their%20supporters%20were%20penned%20into%20crude%20townships%20and%20camps%20that%20sprang%20up%20around%20such%20barricades%2C%20which%20included%20barbed%20wire%20fences%20and%20shipping%20containers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrips%20of%20nails%20have%20been%20placed%20on%20roads%20to%20puncture%20the%20tyres%20of%20vehicles%20farmers%20may%20use%20to%20push%20past%20the%20barricade%3B%20this%20also%20means%20those%20not%20part%20of%20the%20protest%20and%20simply%20looking%20to%20travel%20into%20Delhi%20for%20work%20or%20other%20purposes%2C%20will%20face%20lengthy%20delays%20while%20police%20check%20each%20car%20or%20truck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20has%20hit%20out%20at%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20government%20over%20the%20anti-protest%20measures%3B%20%26quot%3BIs%20the%20laying%20nails%20in%20the%20path%20of%20farmers%20'%3Cem%3Eamritkaal%3C%2Fem%3E'%20or%20'%3Cem%3Eanyaykaal%3C%2Fem%3E'%3F%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20asked%20on%20X%2C%20attacking%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20for%20not%20fulfilling%20promises%20to%20farmers.%20%26quot%3BMr%20Prime%20Minister!%20Why%20such%20behaviour%20with%20the%20country's%20farmers%3F%20Why%20don't%20you%20fulfil%20the%20promises...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flaying-nails-in-farmers-path-amritkaal-or-anyaykaal-priyanka-gandhi-5037219%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELaying%20Nails%20In%20Farmers'%20Path%20'%3Cem%3EAmritkaal%3C%2Fem%3E'%20Or%20'%3Cem%3EAnyaykaal%3C%2Fem%3E'%3A%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20many%20as%201%2C500%20police%20personnel%20will%20be%20deployed%20in%20each%20of%20these%20border%20areas.%20However%2C%20the%20pattern%20of%20deployment%20and%20number%20of%20personnel%20will%20change%20as%20per%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20police%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana-Punjab%20border%20crossings%20in%20Ambala%2C%20Jind%2C%20and%20Fatehabad%20districts%20have%20also%20been%20sealed%2C%20and%20the%20former%20government%20has%20also%20suspended%20f%20mobile%20internet%20services%20and%20bulk%20SMS%20in%20these%20and%20four%20other%20districts%20-%20Kurukshetra%2C%20Kaithal%2C%20Hisar%2C%20and%20Sirsa%20-%20ahead%20of%20the%20farmers'%20proposed%20march.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20government%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-converts-2-stadiums-into-temporary-jails-ahead-of-farmers-march-to-delhi-5038447%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econverted%20two%20large%20stadiums%20into%20temporary%20jails%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20house%20detained%2Farrested%20farmers%20-%20another%20eerie%20replay%20from%20the%202020%2F21%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-delhi-police-tractor-rehearsals-teargas-drills-delhi-cops-prep-for-farmers-protest-5035807%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Cops'%20Farmers'%20Protest%20Drill%20Leaves%20Residents%20In%20Tears%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20police%20are%20practising%20firing%20teargas%20shells%3B%20a%20video%20accessed%20by%20NDTV%20shows%20cops%20firing%20teargas%20shells%20in%20an%20open%20area%20in%20north%20Delhi%2C%20an%20exercise%20that%20left%20area%20residents%20in%20discomfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20-%20facing%20a%20general%20election%20in%20a%20few%20weeks%20-%20is%20understandably%20eager%20to%20resolve%20this%20matter%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible.%20Three%20union%20ministers%2C%20including%20the%20junior%20Agriculture%20Minister%20Arjun%20Munda%20-%20will%20meet%20protesting%20farmers%20later%20today.%20A%20first%20meeting%20was%20held%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707722580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F48a28jsg_delhi-border-security_625x