-drama-list-park-min-young-lee-yi-kyung-dominate-the-actor-list%2Farticleshow%2F107619404.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Rivals%20Plan%20To%20Shun%20Out%20Imran%20Khan%20Allies%20After%20Pak%20Poll%20Results%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20two%20main%20family-controlled%20political%20parties%20are%20drawing%20closer%20to%20forming%20a%20coalition%20government%20that%20would%20thwart%20Imran%20Khan's%20group%2C%20even%20after%20the%20jailed%20former%20cricket%20star's%20candidates%20won%20the%20most%20seats%20in%20the%20country's%20contentious%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parties%20of%20the%20Sharif%20and%20Bhutto%20clans%20%26quot%3Bagreed%20in%20principle%20to%20save%20the%20country%20from%20political%20instability%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20X%20last%20night%20by%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20President%20Shehbaz%20Sharif.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scenario%20would%20be%20a%20closing%20of%20ranks%20by%20Pakistan's%20old%20guard%20after%20Khan's%20loyalists%20-%20running%20as%20independents%20-%20defied%20the%20odds%20with%20a%20strong%20performance%20in%20Thursday's%20election%2C%20showing%20the%20public's%20enduring%20support%20for%20Khan%20and%20disillusionment%20with%20the%20status%20quo.%20It%20could%20also%20lead%20to%20more%20protests%20and%20unrest%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sharifs'%20PML-N%20and%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari's%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20held%20meetings%20over%20the%20past%20two%20days%20as%20they%20seek%20to%20form%20a%20coalition%20after%20the%20election%20resulted%20in%20another%20hung%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhutto%20Zardari's%20party%20said%20it%20would%20consider%20PML-N's%20proposal%20at%20a%20Monday%20meeting%20of%20its%20leadership.%20Sharif%20%26quot%3Bsought%20the%20help%26quot%3B%20of%20Bhutto%20Zardari%2C%20the%20son%20of%20assassinated%20former%20premier%20Benazir%20Bhutto%2C%20to%20form%20a%20government%2C%20the%20PPP%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20party%20disclosed%20the%20details%20of%20the%20proposal%2C%20instead%20posting%20videos%20of%20members%20of%20the%20two%20families%20embracing%20and%20holding%20talks%20in%20the%20sprawling%20Bhutto%20Zardari%20residence%20in%20Lahore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20coalition%20of%20the%20two%20political%20clans%20could%20raise%20tensions%20after%20an%20already%20contentious%20election%2C%20which%20saw%20Khan's%20candidates%2C%20forced%20to%20run%20as%20independents%2C%20shock%20observers%20by%20winning%20the%20most%20seats%20but%20falling%20short%20of%20a%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20delays%20in%20forming%20a%20government%20would%20weigh%20on%20an%20economy%20already%20challenged%20on%20several%20fronts.%20Inflation%20is%20running%20at%2028%25%2C%20the%20fastest%20pace%20in%20Asia%2C%20and%20the%20latest%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20bailout%20program%20is%20set%20to%20expire%20in%20March%2C%20suggesting%20the%20next%20leader%20will%20have%20to%20negotiate%20a%20new%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIrregularities%20and%20a%20delay%20in%20election%20results%20could%20start%20a%20legal%20battle%20and%20this%20situation%20can%20also%20jeopardize%20the%20economic%20outlook%20in%20the%20short%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Adnan%20Khan%2C%20head%20of%20international%20sales%20at%20Intermarket%20Securities%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImran%20Khan's%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20party%2C%20or%20PTI%2C%20is%20set%20to%20file%20suits%20against%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20attempt%20to%20force%20recounts%20in%20some%20National%20Assembly%20seats%20that%20it%20lost.%20Party%20supporters%20have%20held%20small%20protests%20across%20cities%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20blocked%20a%20motorway%20in%20Peshawar%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20election%20rigging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20they%20going%20to%20do%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20put%20everybody%20in%20jail%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20Humaira%20Mahmud%2C%2054%2C%20an%20American-Pakistani%20watching%20from%20the%20sidelines.%20%26quot%3BWe%20love%20our%20army.%20We%20love%20our%20policemen.%20We%20don't%20love%20those%20handful%20of%20generals%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20control%20for%20their%20own%20good.%20They%20need%20to%20be%20respectful%20to%20their%20citizens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20has%20ruled%20Pakistan%20directly%20or%20behind%20the%20scenes%20for%20most%20the%20country's%20modern%20history%20but%20said%20recently%20it%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20involved%20in%20politics.%20Khan%20has%20said%20the%20generals%20conspired%20with%20other%20political%20parties%20to%20oust%20him%20from%20power%20in%20April%202022%20and%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20crackdown%20against%20him%20and%20his%20group%2C%20allegations%20the%20military%20have%20repeatedly%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20military%20establishment%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20politicians%20join%20hands%20and%20refuse%20the%20transfer%20of%20power%20then%20the%20anger%20will%20boil%20over%20to%20the%20streets%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sarwar%20Bari%2C%20an%20Islamabad-based%20political%20analyst%20and%20former%20head%20of%20Free%20and%20Fair%20Election%20Network.%20%26quot%3BThe%20majority%20is%20with%20the%20PTI%20despite%20all%20the%20odds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20loyalists%20took%20at%20least%2095%20of%20the%20265%20National%20Assembly%20seats%20that%20were%20up%20for%20grabs.%20But%20one%20Khan-backed%20candidate%20who%20won%20in%20the%20Sharif%20stronghold%20of%20Lahore%20has%20already%20switched%20sides%20to%20join%20PML-N%2C%20and%20it's%20possible%20others%20may%20also%20change%20allegiances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPTI%20Chairman%20Gohar%20Khan%20told%20local%20TV%20channel%20Geo%20Television%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20independent%20candidates%20%26quot%3Bare%20in%20touch%20with%20us%20and%20will%20stay%20with%20us%20only.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20ruled%20out%20forging%20a%20alliance%20with%20PML-N%20or%20the%20PPP.%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20better%20to%20sit%20in%20the%20opposition%20than%20to%20make%20a%20government%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20a%20Dawn%20News%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707719700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fes8vejbk_imran-khan-supporters-reuters_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-elections-imran-khan-shehbaz-sharif-bilawal-bhutto-how-rivals-plan-to-shun-out-imran-khan-allies-after-pak-poll-results-5041526%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan's%20two%20main%20family-controlled%20political%20parties%20are%20drawing%20closer%20to%20forming%20a%20coalition%20government%20that%20would%20thwart%20Imran%20Khan's%20group%2C%20even%20after%20the%20jailed%20former%20cricket%20star's%20candidates%20won%20the%20most%20seats.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-elections-imran-khan-shehbaz-sharif-bilawal-bhutto-how-rivals-plan-to-shun-out-imran-khan-allies-after-pak-poll-results-5041526%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-elections-imran-khan-shehbaz-sharif-bilawal-bhutto-how-rivals-plan-to-shun-out-imran-khan-allies-after-pak-poll-results-5041526%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-elections-imran-khan-shehbaz-sharif-bilawal-bhutto-how-rivals-plan-to-shun-out-imran-khan-allies-after-pak-poll-results-5041526%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Latest%20In%20DMK%20vs%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Governor%3A%20He%20Doesn't%20Deliver%20Customary%20Speech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20flashpoint%20between%20the%20MK%20Stalin%20government%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%20Governor%20RN%20Ravi%20today%20refused%20to%20deliver%20the%20customary%20address%20to%20the%20Assembly%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20first%20session%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20translation%20of%20the%20speech%20prepared%20by%20the%20state%20government%2C%20which%20reviewed%20its%20work%20and%20outlined%20the%20agenda%20for%20the%20session%2C%20was%20read%20by%20Speaker%20M%20Appavu.%20The%20Governor%20did%20not%20even%20wait%20for%20the%20national%20anthem%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20speech%20and%20walked%20out%20in%20a%20huff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20the%20exit%20when%20senior%20DMK%20Minister%20Durai%20Murugan%20moved%20a%20resolution%20to%20not%20record%20the%20Governor's%20remarks%20and%20it%20was%20adopted.%20Responding%20to%20the%20Governor's%20remarks%2C%20Mr%20Appavu%20said%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%20has%20followed%20a%20tradition%20of%20playing%20the%20state%20anthem%20%26quot%3BThamizh%20Thai%20Vaazhthu%26quot%3B%20before%20the%20Governor's%20address%20and%20the%20national%20anthem%20after%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Speaker%20said%20personal%20opinions%20should%20not%20be%20shared%20in%20the%20House%20and%20added%20that%20the%20Governor%20could%20instead%20get%20the%20Centre%20to%20release%20a%20Rs%2050%2C000%20crore%20flood%20relief%20from%20the%20PM%20Cares%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20too%2C%20dramatic%20scenes%20had%20played%20out%20during%20the%20Governor's%20address%20when%20he%20skipped%20portions%20of%20the%20official%20speech%20prepared%20by%20the%20ruling%20DMK.%20He%20had%20not%20mentioned%20parts%20of%20the%20address%20that%20mentioned%20leaders%20such%20as%20Periyar%2C%20BR%20Ambedkar%2C%20K%20Kamaraj%2C%20CN%20Annadurai%2C%20and%20K%20Karunanidhi.%20Chief%20Minister%20Stalin%20had%20responded%20by%20moving%20a%20resolution%20to%20record%20only%20the%20official%20speech.%20The%20Governor%20had%20then%20walked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Governor's%20refusal%20to%20deliver%20the%20customary%20address%20is%20the%20latest%20face-off%20between%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20and%20the%20DMK%20government%2C%20which%20has%20repeatedly%20accused%20the%20Governor%20of%20creating%20hurdles%20in%20its%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Governor%20and%20the%20state%20government%20were%20locked%20in%20a%20tug%20of%20war%2C%20with%20the%20latter%20accusing%20him%20of%20acting%20like%20a%20BJP%20spokesperson%20and%20not%20clearing%20Bills%20and%20appointments.%20The%20Governor%20had%20then%20said%20the%20Constitution%20empowers%20him%20to%20indefinitely%20withhold%20Bills.%20The%20matter%20had%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20ruled%20that%20the%20Governor%20must%20act%20on%20the%20aid%20and%20advice%20of%20the%20Council%20of%20Ministers.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20Governor%20had%20cleared%20some%20of%20the%20Bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tussle%20had%20also%20reached%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%2C%20when%20Chief%20Minister%20Stalin%20wrote%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20last%20year%2C%20seeking%20Mr%20Ravi's%20removal%20from%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Stalin%20has%20accused%20the%20Governor%20of%20breaching%20his%20oath%20of%20office%20by%20acting%20against%20the%20state's%20people%20and%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Governor%20searching%20for%20an%20opportunity%20to%20bring%20down%20an%20Opposition-ruled%20state%20government%20will%20only%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bagent%20of%20the%20Centre%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20had%20said.%20Mr%20Stalin%20had%20also%20flagged%20the%20Governor's%20action%20to%20dismiss%20Senthil%20Balaji%20as%20a%20minister%20after%20he%20was%20arrested%20by%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%20The%20Governor%20had%20accused%20Mr%20Stalin%20of%20%26quot%3Bunhealthy%20bias%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Senthil%20Balaji%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707719580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2F1njq5noo_mk-stalin-rn-ravi_625x300_09_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https