0Hamad%20Al%20Thani.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20appreciate%20the%20decision%20by%20the%20Amir%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Qatar%20to%20enable%20the%20release%20and%20home-coming%20of%20these%20nationals%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fmedia-briefings.htm%3Fdtl%2F37587%2FTranscript%2Bof%2BWeekly%2BMedia%2BBriefing%2Bby%2Bthe%2BOfficial%2BSpokesperson%2BFebruary%2B08%2B2024%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20last%20weekly%20media%20briefing%20on%20February%208%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20MEA%20spokesperson%20had%20said%20that%20they%20were%20still%20looking%20at%20whether%20to%20lodge%20an%20appeal%20against%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20turning%20the%20death%20sentence%20into%20multiple%20prison%20sentences.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Qatar%20situation%2C%20the%20situation%20as%20far%20as%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20remains%20the%20same%20as%20what%20I%20had%20informed%20you%20earlier.%20There%20is%20a%2060-day%20window%20within%20which%20this%20process%20of%20appeal%20has%20to%20be%20filed.%20So%20that%20is%20where%20we%20are.%20The%20situation%20has%20not%20changed.%20We%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20family%20members.%20We%20are%20also%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20legal%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20MEA%20spokesperson%20had%20said%20four%20days%20ago.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fqatar-8-navy-veterans-hubris-india-diplomacy%5C%22%3ESaving%20the%20Qatar%208%3A%20Did%20Hubris%20Hurt%20India%E2%80%99s%20Diplomacy%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20eight%20naval%20veterans%2C%20who%20had%20been%20detained%20since%20August%202022%2C%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fqatar-eight-former-indian-navy-officers-handed-death-penalty%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esentenced%20to%20death%3C%2