ashed%20out%20at%20the%20Modi%20government%20when%20he%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CInjustice%20is%20being%20served%20to%20south%20India%E2%80%A6%20funds%20that%20were%20supposed%20to%20reach%20the%20south%20are%20getting%20diverted%20and%20distributed%20to%20north%20India.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20the%20clincher%20came%20when%20he%20said%20there%20was%20no%20other%20choice%20but%20to%20ask%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cseparate%20country%E2%80%A6%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20situation%20that%20Hindi%20region%20has%20imposed%20on%20south%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20set%20off%20cries%20of%20outrage%20and%20fury%20in%20the%20Modi%20establishment%20as%20leaders%2C%20MPs%20and%20the%20BJP%20troll%20army%20denounced%20Suresh%20as%20a%20secessionist%20and%20anti-national%20out%20to%20break%20the%20country%20into%20north%20and%20south.%20The%20Congress%20leadership%20went%20from%20first%20denouncing%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20statement%20when%20party%20president%20Mallikarjuna%20Kharge%20said%20that%20anyone%20speaking%20of%20splitting%20the%20country%20will%20not%20be%20tolerated%2C%20to%20party%20spokespersons%20saying%20later%20that%20Suresh%20may%20have%20been%20inarticulate%20in%20wanting%20a%20separate%20country%20for%20the%20south%20but%20fiscal%20unfairness%20to%20the%20south%20was%20real.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Suresh%20clarified%20he%E2%80%99s%20a%20proud%20Indian%20but%20will%20continue%20to%20fight%20against%20injustice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarely%20a%20few%20days%20later%2C%20on%20February%206%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20splashed%20full-page%20ads%20in%20national%20dailies%20for%20%E2%80%98Chalo%20Delhi%E2%80%99%2C%20asking%20people%20to%20march%20with%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20Shivakumar%20and%20all%20147%20MLAs%20%E2%80%9Cto%20protest%20against%20the%20financial%20atrocities%20by%20the%20Central%20government%20on%20Kannadigas%20and%20Karnataka%E2%80%9D.%20The%20chief%20minister%20also%20invited%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20from%20the%20state%20saying%20the%20protest%20was%20%E2%80%9Capolitical%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20it%20was%20about%20safeguarding%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20Chalo%20Delhi%20become%20the%20new%20INDIA%20slogan%2C%20in%20more%20ways%20than%20one%3F%20While%20the%20Karnataka%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20boisterous%20protest%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Jantar%20Mantar%20got%20the%20usually%20reluctant%20media%20to%20actually%20report%20and%20examine%20the%20allegations%20of%20fiscal%20unfairness%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20too%20got%20into%20action%20%E2%80%93%20with%20both%20Sitharaman%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%20lambasting%20the%20Congress%20particularly%20in%20Parliament%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Budget%20session%2C%20accusing%20the%20party%20of%20propagating%20lies%2C%20and%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20a%20politically%20vitiated%20narrative%20of%20some%20vested%20interests.%20Sitharaman%20flatly%20said%20that%20no%20one%20can%20deny%20funds%20earmarked%20for%20states%20by%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%20as%20per%20its%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20was%20equally%20vehement%20when%20he%20slammed%20the%20Congress%2C%20saying%20in%20Parliament%2C%20%E2%80%9CDivisive%20politics%20over%20government%20funds%20is%20dangerous.%20Our%20tax%2C%20our%20money%2C%20what%20kind%20of%20language%20is%20this%3F%20Stop%20searching%20for%20narratives%20to%20break%20the%20nation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Funny%2C%20but%20in%20the%20same%20speech%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20recalled%20his%20time%20as%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat%20to%20stress%20his%20commitment%20to%20federalism%20when%20he%20said%20he%20%E2%80%9Cunderstands%20regional%20aspirations%E2%80%9D.%20Of%20course%2C%20he%20underlined%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Congress-led%20UPA%20government%20at%20the%20time%20%E2%80%9Ctried%20its%20best%20to%20do%20injustice%20to%20Gujarat%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20cry%20over%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStates%20give%20back%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20what%20if%20regional%20chief%20ministers%20decided%20to%20clone%20chief%20minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20bold%20and%20unabashed%20bid%20as%20in%202014%20as%20Vikas%20Purush%20or%20Development%20Man%2C%20of%20making%20brand%20Vibrant%20Gujarat%20go%20global%20even%20while%20stressing%20on%20Gujarat%20Asmita%20and%20pride%3F%20After%20all%2C%20it%20was%20a%20beleaguered%20chief%20minister%20then%20who%20had%20the%20ghost%20of%20Godhra%20and%20its%20murderous%20riots%20of%202002%20follow%20him%20persistently%2C%20yet%2012%20years%20later%2C%20Modi%20has%20catapulted%20himself%20on%20centre%20stage%20after%20a%20year%20of%20a%20constant%20and%20an%20extravagant%20re-branding%20venture%2C%20from%20a%20regional%2C%20divisive%20leader%20to%20a%20decisive%20development%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20if%20Karnataka%20has%20to%20take%20a%20cue%20from%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20rebranding%20strategy%2C%20it%20only%20has%20to%20turn%20the%20Modi%20tactics%20on%20their%20head%20and%20focus%20on%20how%20the%20Centre%20is%20depriving%20an%20already%20developed%20state%20because%20of%20its%20discriminatory%20practices.%20The%20Siddaramaiah-Shivakumar%20duo%20has%20calculated%20a%20financial%20loss%20of%20an%20astounding%20Rs%201.87%20lakh%20crore%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%20because%20of%20the%20formula%20defined%20by%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%2C%20as%20the%20state%20gets%20a%20paltry%20Rs%2013%20for%20every%20Rs%20100%20it%20collects%20in%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20Siddaramaiah%20who%20first%20raised%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Canomalies%20in%20federal%20fiscal%20transfers%E2%80%9D%20when%20he%20spoke%20at%20a%20national%20seminar%20on%20fiscal%20federalism%20on%20January%2020%20this%20year%2C%20on%20the%20challenges%20before%20his%20government%20in%20sustaining%20an%20inclusive%20and%20balanced%20economic%20growth%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20budgetary%20implications%20of%20centrally-sponsored%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKarnataka%20has%20experienced%20the%20biggest%20cut%20among%20states%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdespite%20being%20the%20second%20highest%20tax%20paying%20state%20after%20Maharashtra%2C%20yet%20it%20does%20not%20get%20adequate%20reward%20for%20its%20contribution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22'Fiscal%20Injustice'%20Powers%20a%20New%20Axis%20of%20Protest%20Against%20Modi%20Govt%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffiscal-injustice-powers-a-new-axis-of-protest-against-modi-govt%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Fiscal%20Injustice%E2%80%99%20Powers%20a%20New%20Axis%20of%20Protest%20Against%20Modi%20Govt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20about%20some%20Kannadiga%20Hemmeya%20or%20pride%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20Silicon%20Valley%E2%80%99s%20hi-tech%20and%20start%20up%20glitz%20and%20geek%20squad%20who%20never%20tire%20of%20their%20newfound%20status%20as%20a%20proud%20Indian%20both%20at%20home%20and%20abroad%3F%20Techies%20and%20the%20cyber%20crew%20today%20believe%20the%20Indian%20passport%20carries%20pride%20and%20self-esteem%2C%20and%20rightly%20so%2C%20but%20pop%20neo-nationalism%20does%20not%20stop%20at%20wearing%20patriotism%20on%20the%20sleeve%20but%20pride%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20state%2C%20region%20and%20distinct%20culture.%20If%20the%20citizens%20of%20the%20state%20capital%20have%20deplored%20the%20calamitous%20and%20crashing%20infrastructure%20because%20of%20poor%2C%20unplanned%20growth%2C%20even%20as%20concerned%20groups%20have%20raised%20alarm%20about%20the%20inequities%20in%20the%20rural%20areas%2C%20imagine%20the%20transformation%20and%20progress%20that%20can%20be%20waved%20in%20with%20due%20allotment%20to%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EForging%20a%20united%20fiscal%20front%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20state%20assembly%20polls%20last%20year%20was%20defined%20by%20a%20divisive%20Hindu-Muslim%20campaign%20when%20a%20pliant%20media%20was%20agog%20with%20hijab%20bans%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges%2C%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20and%20Tipu%20Sultan%2C%20though%20it%20flopped%20at%20the%20polls%3B%20what%20if%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20campaign%20focused%20on%20a%20people%E2%80%99s%20movement%2C%20focusing%20on%20development%20and%20only%20development%20and%20making%20it%20a%20demand%20of%20the%20people%2C%20as%20economic%20and%20social%20progress%2C%20growth%2C%20revival%20and%20upliftment%20all%20depend%20on%20Central%20funds%20owed%20to%20the%20state%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reverberations%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20protest%20are%20already%20being%20felt%20in%20other%20states%20%E2%80%93%20a%20day%20later%2C%20on%20February%208%2C%20Kerala%20led%20the%20protest%20in%20Jantar%20Mantar%20when%20chief%20minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20staged%20a%20similar%20protest%20saying%20the%20state%20had%20lost%20around%20Rs%2057%2C000%20crore%20because%20of%20the%20end%20of%20GST%20compensation%2C%20reduction%20in%20tax%20share%20and%20loan%20disallowance.%20Pinaryi%20Vijayan%20got%20Opposition%20leaders%20to%20share%20the%20protest%20stage%20with%20him%3A%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20from%20AAP%3B%20CPI(M)%20leader%20Sitaram%20Yechury%3B%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20minister%20Farooq%20Abdulla%3B%20and%20D.%20Raja%20from%20the%20CPI.%20The%20DMK%20held%20a%20protest%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20chief%20minister%20M.K.%20Stalin%2C%20a%20major%20detractor%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20policies%2C%20expressed%20solidarity%20when%20he%20deputed%20cabinet%20colleague%20P.T.%20Rajan%20to%20the%20Kerala%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20fairly%20noticeable%20that%20non-Congress%20Opposition%20leaders%20staged%20their%20protest%20on%20a%20separate%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20also%20be%20said%20here%20that%20the%20Kerala%20government%20had%20filed%20a%20suit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20January%2012%2C%20desperately%20seeking%20the%20urgent%20release%20of%20funds%20for%20employee%20wages%2C%20flood%20rehabilitation%20and%20development%20work.%20The%20attorney%20general%20representing%20the%20Modi%20government%20opposed%20the%20plea%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThirty-three%20states%20have%20no%20issues%2C%20just%20one%20state%20has%20all%20the%20issues.%E2%80%9D%20The%20court%20has%20asked%20the%20Modi%20%7Cgovernment%20for%20a%20reply%20to%20the%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Telangana%2C%20newly%20elected%20Congress%20chief%20minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%20in%20the%20assembly%20yesterday%20appealed%20to%20all%20MLAs%20including%20the%20Opposition%20to%20join%20hands%20together%20to%20protect%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20interests%20by%20setting%20aside%20politics.%20Replying%20to%20a%20debate%20on%20the%20motion%20of%20thanks%20to%20the%20governor%2C%20Reddy%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTelangana%20is%20not%20just%20geography%20but%20an%20emotion%20of%20four%20crore%20people.%E2%80%9D%20The%20AIMIM%20was%20swift%20to%20extend%20support%20to%20the%20Congress%20government%20if%20minority%20rights%20were%20protected%2C%20said%20AIMIM%20leader%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20Akbaruddin%20Owaisi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20true%20are%20the%20allegations%20of%20discriminatory%20fiscal%20allotments%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20non-BJP%20ruled%20states%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20states%20that%20have%20been%20complaining%20of%20fiscal%20discrimination%20by%20the%20Centre%20have%20clearly%20outlined%20that%20they%20have%20no%20grouse%20against%20poorer%20states%20getting%20more%20funds%20to%20meet%20their%20expenditure.%20All%20they%20are%20saying%20is%20to%20simply%20give%20them%20their%20dues%20and%20not%20penalise%20them%20for%20not%20being%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%20or%20its%20ally.%20Dues%20should%20be%20paid%20according%20to%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%20criteria%20(45%25%20for%20income%20distance%2C%2015%25%20for%20population%2C%2015%25%20for%20area%2C%2010%25%20for%20forest%20and%20ecology%2C%2012.5%25%20for%20demographic%20performance%20and%202.5%25%20for%20tax%20effort).%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20shown%20how%20the%20Centre%20has%20tied%20them%20in%20knots%20by%20penalising%20or%20simply%20not%20returning%20the%20funds%20due%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Garvi%20Gujarat%20and%20Vikas%20Purush%20have%20given%20a%20fillip%20to%20regional%20players%20perhaps%20the%20fault%20lines%20today%20lie%20with%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20touted%20%E2%80%98Double%20Engine%20Sarkar%E2%80%99%20slogan%3F%20After%20all%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20along%20with%20a%20fawning%20media%20have%20promoted%20the%20electoral%20battle%20cry%2C%20%E2%80%98Vote%20Modi%20in%20the%20Centre%20and%20states%2C%20for%20development%E2%80%99.%20Or%20else%20perish.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707701421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11170335%2FGFzlNlYbAAAyYbL.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnew-frontlines-before-elections-force-modi-govt-to-be-answerable-on-bread-and-butter-issues%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Modi%20government%20would%20want%20to%20lead%20off%20into%20the%20general%20elections%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20the%20Mandir%20and%20other%20allied%20issues.%20After%20a%20ten-year%20stay%20at%20the%20wheels%20of%20power%2C%20could%20several%20states%20making%20a%20popular%20case%20about%20a%20Centre%20that%20does%20not%20hold%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20upset%20the%20Modi%20applecart%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnew-frontlines-before-elections-force-modi-govt-to-be-answerable-on-bread-and-butter-issues%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Every%20song%20on%20Usher's%20setlist%20for%20the%20Super%