3724923_n-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20has%20slapped%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20against%20Sameer%20Wankhede%2C%20a%20former%20IRS%20officer%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20demanding%20a%20Rs%2025%20crore%20bribe%20from%20actor%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20for%20not%20framing%20his%20son%20in%20a%20drug%20case%20in%20October%202021%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fed-files-money-laundering-case-against-sameer-wankhede-101707536892377.html%5C%22%3Enews%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20on%20February%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWankhede%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20approached%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20to%20seek%20protection%20from%20coercive%20action%20until%20the%20case%20is%20heard%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fhigh-court%2Fbombay-high-court%2Fsameer-wankhede-bombay-high-court-ed-money-laundering-cordelia-cruise-drugs-case-ncb-249148%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ELive%20Law%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Flaw%2Fhigh-courts%2Fstory%2Faryan-khan-drug-case-sameer-wankhede-moves-court-seeking-protection-from-arrest-2500150-2024-02-10%23%5C%22%3Eheard%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20February%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EED%20files%20money%20laundering%20case%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20case%20is%20based%20on%20a%202023%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%2C%20which%20alleged%20that%20Wankhede%2C%20a%20former%20zonal%20director%20of%20Narcotics%20Control%20Bureau%2C%20was%20among%20the%20four%20people%20who%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20demanding%20a%20Rs%2025%20crore%20bribe%20from%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20for%20not%20framing%20his%20son%2C%20Aryan%20Khan%2C%20in%20a%20October%202021%20drug%20case.%20Wankhede%20had%20led%20the%20raids%20aboard%20a%20docked%20cruise%