0for%20certain%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20jury%2C%20led%20by%20Justice%20Madan%20B.%20Lokur%20and%20including%20prominent%20figures%20like%20Riyad%20Mathew%20and%20Shobhaa%20De%2C%20recognised%20the%20duo%20for%20uncovering%20the%20digital%20ecosystem%20that%20disseminates%20divisive%20narratives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journalists%20highlighted%20how%20individuals%20appeared%20in%20various%20roles%20across%20videos%20to%20promote%20specific%20political%20agendas%2C%20illustrating%20a%20symbiotic%20relationship%20between%20YouTubers%20and%20political%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20lot%20of%20cases%2C%20the%20same%20individual%20appeared%20in%20different%20roles%20in%20videos%20pushing%20a%20particular%20political%20narrative.%20It%20is%20a%20symbiotic%20relationship%20wherein%20the%20YouTubers%20are%20earning%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20and%20the%20political%20parties%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20propaganda%20content%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20two%20winners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Week%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fnews%2Findia%2F2024%2F02%2F09%2Ffreelance-journalists-neel-madhav-alishan-jafri-win-ipi-india-award-for-excellence-in-journalism.html%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Justice%20Lokur%2C%20who%20presided%20over%20the%20function%2C%20as%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9COver%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20we%20have%20had%20an%20overdose%20of%20hate.%20In%20most%20instances%2C%20it%20was%20restricted%20to%20hate%20speech%2C%20but%20soon%20the%20venom%20became%20more%20poisonous%20and%20resulted%20in%20violence%20against%20innocent%20persons%2C%20including%20youngsters.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20restrictive%20or%20coercive%20action%20by%20the%20police%2C%20vigilante%20groups%20got%20emboldened%20and%20the%20consequence%20was%20an%20outbreak%20of%20lynching.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20an%20unintended%20consequence%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20giving%20directions%20on%20the%20matter%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20data%20about%20lynching%20vanished%20from%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20and%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20stopped%20collecting%20data%20on%20lynching.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEminent%20jurist%20F.S.%20Nariman%2C%20while%20presenting%20the%20award%2C%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20decline%20of%20press%20freedom%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20past%20the%20age%20of%20free%20speech%20and%20entering%20another%20age%20%E2%80%93%20an%20age%20of%20thought%20control.%20You%20will%20say%20what%20thought-control%20prompts%20you%20to%20say.%20It%20is%20a%20serious%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20after%20watching%20a%20video%20made%20by%20the%20two%20award-winning%20scribes%20on%20how%20they%20exposed%20rackets%20that%20were%20making%20fake%20videos%20and%20spreading%20hate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20drop%20in%20the%20world%20press%20freedom%20index%20is%20that%20governments%20at%20the%20Centre%20or%20state%20operate%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20much%20of%20the%20media%20are%20compelled%20to%20look%20over%20their%20shoulder%20to%20see%20if%20government%20officials%20are%20smiling%20at%20them.%20The%20condition%20is%20not%20at%20all%20suited%20for%20a%20free%20press%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nariman.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707653118000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11171229%2Fimage-1823.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fneel-madhav-and-alishan-jafri-win-ipi-india-award-for-excellence-in-journalism-in-the-caravan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Their%20story%2C%20titled%20'Clicks%20and%20Bait'%2C%20exposed%20how%20a%20group%20of%20YouTubers%20were%20setting%20the%20agenda%20for%20television%20debates%20and%20creating%20bulk%20content%20for%20certain%20political%20parties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A45%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22ht