king%20is%20that%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20is%20directly%20and%20morally%20implicated%20in%20this%20extra-constitutional%20event%20as%20a%20Union%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20Rajkumar%20Ranjan%20Singh%2C%20the%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20External%20Affairs%20%E2%80%93%20was%20also%20amongst%20the%20functionaries%20who%20took%20the%20oath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20by%20the%20logic%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20anti-terror%20law%2C%20Arambai%E2%80%99s%20actions%20from%20May%203%20onwards%20(and%2C%20specifically%20the%20January%2024%20event)%20amount%20to%20%E2%80%9Cterrorist%20act(s)%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20threat%20to%20national%20security.%20Their%20actions%20fall%20squarely%20within%20the%20four%20corners%20of%20what%20is%20punishable%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20(UAPA)%2C%201967.%20They%20were%20undertaken%2C%20among%20others%2C%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cintent%20to%20strike%20terror%20in%20the%20people%E2%80%9D%20and%20to%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6compel%20the%20State%20Government%20or%20the%20Government%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%20to%20fulfil%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Arambai%20is%20yet%20to%20face%20the%20music%20from%20the%20state.%20Let%20alone%20legal%20action%2C%20the%20Manipur%20police%20has%20not%20detained%20a%20single%20member%20of%20the%20armed%20group%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Coath-taking%E2%80%9D%20ceremony%20and%20the%20alleged%20violence%20against%20elected%20lawmakers.%20Neither%20has%20the%20state%20government%2C%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20chief%20minister%2C%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20condemned%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-a-land-of-settled-grief%5C%22%3EManipur%3A%20A%20Land%20of%20Settled%20Grief%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Robinhood%20militia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20Imphal%20and%20New%20Delhi%20have%20watched%20from%20the%20wings%20as%20