nipur%20since%20May%20as%20being%20akin%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F06%2F09%2Fa-pen-can-do-more-harm-than-a-gun-in-manipur-meitei-owned-media-is-winning-the-perception-war%5C%22%3EWhatsApp%20group%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meitei%20public%20now%20sees%20the%20Arambai%20as%20a%20unifying%20political%20force%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20their%20rightful%20military%20representative.%20For%20them%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Coath-taking%E2%80%9D%20ceremony%20was%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20discipline%20Meitei%20lawmakers%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum%20and%20compel%20them%20to%20uphold%20core%20concerns%20of%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20Kangla%20Fort%20event%2C%20with%20all%20its%20spectacular%20symbolism%20and%20political%20iconography%2C%20has%20thickened%20the%20air%20of%20myth%20and%20enigma%20around%20Arambai%20Tenggol%2C%20a%20name%20that%20evocatively%20refers%20to%20the%20dart-wielding%20calvary%20force%20of%20the%20ancient%20Meitei%20kingdom%20of%20Kangleipak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBroad%20appeal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20Arambai%20seems%20to%20have%20become%20even%20more%20popular%20than%20the%20established%20(and%20proscribed)%20Meitei%20armed%20groups%2C%20such%20as%20the%20United%20National%20Liberation%20Front%20(UNLF)%2C%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%2C%20and%20Kanglei%20Yawol%20Kanna%20Lup%20(KYKL).%20It%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20more%20successful%20than%20these%20older%20insurgent%20groups%20in%20drawing%20the%20disenchanted%20and%20disgruntled%20Meitei%20youth%20into%20a%20programme%20of%20patriotism%20and%20direct%20action.%20In%20fact%2C%20even%20in%20terms%20of%20actual%20armed%20action%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20the%20Arambai%20appear%20to%20have%20overshadowed%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20older%20groups%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20potential%20turf%20war%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20more%20worrying%20perhaps%20is%20that%20the%20Arambai%E2%80%99s%20soaring%20influence%20among%20the%20Meiteis%2C%20including%20their%20public%20figures%2C%20will%20further%20discourage%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20from%20acting%20against%20it.%20By%20moving%20against%20the%20group%2C%20Biren%20Singh%20could%20alienate%20his%20core%20constituencies%20and%20thus%2C%20make%20himself%20less%20politically%20valuable%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20high%20command.%20This%20creates%20a%20fatal%20deadlock%2C%20which%20allows%20the%20Arambai%20to%20not%20just%20persist%2C%20but%20also%20grow%20even%20bigger%20and%20stronger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20prominent%20Meitei%20personalities%2C%20such%20as%20Bollywood%20actress%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC2h1D58tWMo%2F%3Figsh%3DMXR3d3AxMWRyeXp1eg%3D%3D%5C%22%3ELin%20Laishram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Licypriya%20Kangujam%2C%20a%2012-year-old%20climate%20activist%2C%20have%20publicly%20expressed%20their%20support%20for%20the%20Arambai%20on%20social%20media.%20Licypriya%20had%20even%20mobilised%20funds%20for%20the%20purchase%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthefrontiermanipur.com%2Fchild-activist-licypriya-hands-over-thermal-drones-items-to-at%2F%5C%22%3Ethermal%20imaging%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20militia%20to%20use%20in%20their%20fight%20against%20what%20she%20called%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20Kuki%20Narco%20Terrorist%E2%80%9D.%20Using%20social%20service%20acts%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fksherson.thoudam%2Fposts%2Fpfbid02dx7VHC69FmiAkXpsWxuUeYz8uFihf6yqME9fij8mzq8qaVkqYDThaSqyneCBhZfMl%5C%22%3Edistributing%20aid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Meitei%20relief%20camps%2C%20the%20Arambai%20has%20been%20able%20to%20command%20wide%20appeal%20in%20Meitei%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECollusion%20with%20state%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarious%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-more-than-five-dead-dozens-injured-over-the-last-two-weeks-amid-ongoing-ethnic-unrest%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20mainstream%20and%20social%20media%20have%20indicated%20that%20the%20Arambai%20enjoys%20high-profile%20patronage%20from%20the%20Meitei%20ruling%20elite.%20Even%20before%20the%20conflict%20began%20in%20May%2C%20it%20had%20the%20attention%20of%20senior%20political%20figures.%20Pictures%20from%20August%202022%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Farambai-tenggol-group-manipur-meitei-mla-9128683%2F%5C%22%3Eshow%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20militia%E2%80%99s%20leader%2C%20Khuman%2C%20sitting%20with%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20Leishemba%20Sanajaoba%2C%20the%20titular%20king%20of%20Manipur%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP.%20A%20Facebook%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHHSanajaoba.Leishemba%2Fvideos%2Foath-taking-ceremony-of-arambai-tenggol-group-at-my-residence250922%2F430995689136627%2F%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20September%20that%20year%20shows%20cadres%20taking%20some%20kind%20of%20oath%20at%20Sanajaoba%E2%80%99s%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zomi%20community%20have%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1050361%2Farmed-gangs-and-a-partisan-state-how-manipur-slipped-into-civil-war%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20state%20police%20of%20providing%20cover%20to%20Arambai%20cadres%20during%20violent%20attacks%20against%20their%20villages.%20Kuki-Zomi%20organisations%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fmanipur%2Fsecurity-forces-struggle-to-recover-snatched-weapons-in-conflict-hit-manipur-2656856%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20police%20of%20handing%20over%20arms%20to%20Arambai%20members%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20have%20openly%20flaunted%20them%20in%20public.%20This%20marks%20a%20sinister%20blurring%20of%20lines%20between%20state%20and%20non-state%20armed%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20why%20has%20this%20happened%3F%20One%20reason%20could%20be%20that%20the%20Manipur%20government%20was%20keen%20on%20delegating%20the%20mandate%20of%20law%20enforcement%20to%20other%20actors.%20But%2C%20there%20may%20be%20other%20factors%20in%20an%20ethnically%20loaded%20context.%20Writing%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F24546330%3Fseq%3D1%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJournal%20of%20Conflict%20Resolution%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sabine%20C.%20Carey%2C%20Michael%20P.%20Colaresi%20and%20Neil%20J.%20Mitchell%20argue%20that%20%E2%80%9Cgovernments%20perceive%20ties%20to%20militias%20as%20a%20mechanism%20to%20evade%20accountability%20and%20muddy%20the%20flow%20of%20information%20about%20who%20is%20responsible%20for%20violence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20reminded%20of%20the%20Arab%20Janjaweed%20militia%20in%20Sudan%2C%20which%2C%20supported%20by%20the%20government%2C%20wreaked%20havoc%20in%20the%20Darfur%20region%20two%20decades%20ago.%20It%20showed%20the%20world%20the%20catastrophic%20consequences%20of%20a%20government%20giving%20%3Cem%3Ecarte%20blanche%3C%2Fem%3E%20(and%20access%20to%20small%20arms)%20to%20an%20ethnic%20militia.%20The%20example%20of%20Libya%20after%202011%20also%20comes%20to%20mind.%20The%20vacuum%20that%20the%20killing%20of%20Muammar%20al-Qaddafi%20by%20NATO-linked%20forces%20left%20was%20quickly%20filled%20up%20by%20various%20militias%2C%20which%20then%20went%20on%20to%20claim%20state%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20one%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20go%20that%20far.%20Right%20next%20to%20Manipur%2C%20the%20Myanmar%20military%20has%20been%20using%20a%20violent%20militia%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprogressivevoicemyanmar.org%2F2022%2F03%2F12%2Fthe-rising-of-pyu-saw-htee%2F%5C%22%3EPyu%20Saw%20Htee%20(PSH)%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20fight%20its%20dirty%20war%20against%20pro-democracy%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-violence-claims-counterclaims-meitei-kuki%5C%22%3EDispelling%20Some%20Misleading%20Claims%20About%20the%20Violence%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArambai%E2%80%99s%20growing%20political%20shadow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20demands%20that%20Arambai%20had%20made%20in%20its%20%E2%80%9Cresolution%E2%80%9D%20during%20the%20Kangla%20event%20was%20fencing%20the%20India-Myanmar%20border.%20It%20had%20given%20New%20Delhi%2015%20days%20to%20fulfil%20the%20demand.%20On%20February%203%2C%20Singh%20travelled%20to%20New%20Delhi%20to%20meet%20Shah%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNBirenSingh%2Fstatus%2F1753733494499332544%5C%22%3Erevealed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20government%20was%20%E2%80%9Cset%20to%20take%20some%20important%20decisions%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20later%2C%20and%2012%20days%20after%20Arambai%20made%20its%20demands%2C%20Shah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findia-to-fence-indo-myanmar-border-says-amit-shah-work-underway-in-arunachal-pradesh-and-manipur-11707231157754.html%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20would%20fence%20the%20entire%20border.%20Two%20days%20later%2C%20he%20announced%20that%20the%20home%20ministry%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmitShah%2Fstatus%2F1755482704152305786%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1755482704152305786%257Ctwgr%255E597147d62001f291c1d58d0a8285008a89cbd22c%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Findianexpress.com%252Farticle%252Findia%252Ffree-movement-regime-india-myanmar-amit-shah-9150557%252F%5C%22%3Esuspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Free%20Movement%20Regime%20(FMR)%20that%20allows%20visa-free%20travel%20along%20the%2016-kilometre%20band%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20wonders%20if%20these%20big-ticket%20decisions%20are%20directly%20linked%20to%20Arambai%E2%80%99s%20demands%20(and%20deadline).%20If%20so%2C%20it%20is%20a%20deeply%20worrying%20sign%20of%20New%20Delhi%20giving%20in%20to%20an%20anarchic%20power%20in%20Manipur.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20sign%20of%20Arambai%E2%80%99s%20political%20sway%20in%20not%20just%20Imphal%2C%20but%20far%20beyond%20it%2C%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20two%20days%20before%20the%20Kangla%20event%2C%20an%20official%20central%20delegation%20composed%20of%20the%20interlocutor%20for%20the%20Kuki-Zomi%20insurgent%20groups%2C%20%5Borganised%20under%20the%20United%20People%E2%80%99s%20Front%20(UPF)%20and%20the%20Kuki%20National%20Organization%20(KNO)%5D%2C%20A.K.%20Mishra%2C%20and%20two%20senior%20officials%20from%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20(IB)%20were%20rushed%20to%20Imphal%20to%20hold%20a%20series%20of%20meetings%20with%20the%20Arambai.%20It%20is%20likely%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20reach%20a%20compromise%20to%20prevent%20a%20coup%20d%E2%80%99etat%20in%20Manipur.%20Clearly%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20too%2C%20can%E2%80%99t%20dismiss%2C%20let%20alone%20challenge%2C%20the%20militia%E2%80%99s%20influence%20in%20Imphal.%20In%20turn%2C%20Arambai%20is%20able%20to%20cement%20its%20credibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerely%20two%20days%20after%20the%20Kangla%20Fort%20event%2C%20the%20state%20government%20hosted%20Republic%20Day%20at%20the%20same%20location.%20In%20his%20speech%2C%20Singh%20paid%20homage%20to%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20and%20urged%20the%20people%20to%20%E2%80%9Crespect%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20and%20one%20another%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D.%E2%80%9D%20The%20absurd%20irony%20isn%E2%80%99t%20lost%20on%20anyone%2C%20one%20hopes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20the%20political%20forces%20behind%20its%20meteoric%20rise%20are%20ultimately%20prosecuted%20or%20not%20is%20a%20different%20matter.%20The%20fact%20remains%20that%20on%20January%2024%2C%20the%20death%20knell%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20rang%20loud%20with%20a%20deafening%20shrillness%20from%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20Kangla%20Fort.%20The%20Modi%20government%20now%20has%20three%20choices%20%E2%80%93%20to%20shut%20the%20din%2C%20to%20shut%20its%20own%20ears%2C%20or%20to%20jive%20along%20with%20it.%20It%20is%20entirely%20up%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20home%20minister%20to%20take%20their%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJohn%20Simte%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Eis%20an%20advocate%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EAngshuman%20Choudhury%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Eis%20an%20Associate%20Fellow%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Research%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707652842000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04223216%2Fimage-968.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-arambai-tenggol-imphal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Whether%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20the%20political%20forces%20behind%20its%20meteoric%20rise%20are%20ultimately%20prosecuted%20or%20not%20is%20a%20different%20matter.%20The%20fact%20remains%20that%20on%20January%2024%2C%20the%20death%20knell%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20rang%20loud%20with%20a%20deafening%20shrillness%20from%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20Kangla%20Fort.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-arambai-tenggol-imphal%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Changing%20Place%20Names%20May%20Soon%20Be%20Punishable%20in%20Manipur%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18103704%2FF6AFcQWaIAIi2H2.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Using%20place%20names%20not%20authorised%20by%20the%20government%20may%20soon%20be%20a%20punishable%20offence%20in%20Manipur.%20A%20Bill%20that%20proposes%20this%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20tabled%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Manipur%20assembly%20session%2C%20as%20per%20a%20news%20report%20by%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fstrife-torn-manipur-new-law-changing-names-places-punishable-9155003%2F%5C%22%3E%20the%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%209%2C%20the%20Manipur%20government%20announced%20that%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20next%20assembly%20session%20will%20begin%20on%20February%2028.%20One%20of%20the%20Bills%20that%20the%20government%20might%20table%20during%20the%20session%20is%20titled%20the%20%E2%80%98Manipur%20Names%20of%20Places%20Bill%2C%202024%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20for%20the%20Bill%20has%20been%20prepared%20by%20the%20Land%20Resources%20Department%20and%20approved%20by%20the%20state%20cabinet%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20news%20report%2C%20dated%20February%2011%2C%20said.%20Per%20the%20report%2C%20the%20objective%20is%20to%20establish%20%E2%80%9Can%20institutional%20mechanism%20to%20enforce%20correct%20use%20of%20names%20of%20places%E2%80%9D%20as%20well%20as%20to%20%E2%80%9Clay%20down%20procedures%20for%20giving%20names%20to%20places%2C%20and%20also%20for%20altering%20names%20of%20places%E2%80%9D.%20Per%20the%20Bill%2C%20offenders%20will%20be%20punished%20with%20a%20penalty%2C%20and%20can%20receive%20one%20to%20three%20years%20of%20imprisonment%20upon%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPer%20the%20new%20Bill%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98Place%20Names%20Committee%E2%80%99%20will%20be%20created%20to%20make%20recommendations%20on%20the%20names%2C%20subject%20to%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20government.%20The%20latest%20news%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20proposal%20for%20the%20Act%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20multiple%20instances%20of%20the%20use%20of%20unauthorised%20names%20of%20places%20by%20certain%20individuals%20or%20groups%20of%20people%20or%20organisations%2C%20with%20possible%20malafide%20intent%2C%20which%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20create%20confusion%20in%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20state.%E2%80%9D%20The%20proposal%20also%20lists%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccertain%20administrative%20challenges%20are%20also%20faced%20due%20to%20such%20unauthorised%20use%20of%20names%20of%20places%20at%20the%20time%20of%20discharging%20their%20duties%20by%20government%20officials%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENames%20of%20places%20have%20been%20a%20contested%20issue%20since%20violence%20began%20in%20Manipur%20in%20May%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20prominent%20example%E2%80%9D%20is%20that%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zomi-dominated%20district%20Churachandpur%20and%20its%20district%20headquarters%2C%20also%20called%20Churachandpur.%20The%20district%20and%20town%20is%20named%20after%20a%20Meitei%20king%20of%20the%20former%20Manipur%20kingdom%2C%20Churachand%20Singh%2C%20who%20ruled%20the%20area%20from%201891%20to%201941.%20But%20people%20from%20the%20Kuki-Zomi%20community%20have%20been%20calling%20the%20town%20%E2%80%9CLamka%E2%80%9D%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Both%20the%20names%20are%20over%20a%20hundred%20years%20old%2C%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20after%20the%20violence%20erupted%2C%20the%20name%20Lamka%20began%20appearing%20on%20homes%2C%20shops%20and%20even%20government%20institutions%20and%20offices.%20Similarly%2C%20resident%20Meiteis%20now%20call%20Paite%20Veng%20(Paite%20is%20a%20Zo%20sub-tribe%20and%20Veng%20means%20colony)%20in%20Imphal%20%E2%80%98Kwakeithel%20Ningthemkol%E2%80%99%20via%20a%20signboard%2C%20the%20news%20report%20highlighted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Manipur%20government%2C%20via%20an%20order%20by%20the%20chief%20secretary%2C%20told%20organisations%20and%20individuals%20to%20not%20change%20names%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdistricts%2C%20sub-divisions%2C%20places%2C%20institutions%2C%20and%20addresses%20of%20such%20institutions%E2%80%9D%20on%20their%20own%20%E2%80%93%20which%20could%20create%20possible%20conflict%20between%20communities%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fdont-change-names-of-places-warns-manipur-government%2Farticle67393496.ece%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20upcoming%20assembly%20session%20will%20be%20only%20the%20second%20so%20far%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20on%20May%203%20last%20year.%20As%20per%20latest%20official%20figures%20%E2%80%93%20as%20of%20September%2015%20last%20year%20%E2%80%93%20the%20violence%20has%20killed%20175%20people%20and%20injured%201%2C118%3B%2032%20people%20are%20still%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707650780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18103704%2FF6AFcQWaIAIi2H2.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fchanging-place-names-may-soon-be-punishable-in-manipur-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Bill%20that%20proposes%20this%20will%20likely%20be%20tabled%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Manipur%20assembly%20session.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fchanging-place-names-may-soon-be-punishable-in-manipur-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20warnings%20from%20Iraq's%20powerful%20armed%20groups%20bode%20badly%20for%20the%20Middle%20East's%20stability%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707632700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-harakat-iraq-us-israeli_6451739.jpg%3F20240211092700%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwhy-warnings-from-iraqs-powerful-armed-groups-bode-badly-for-the-middle-easts-stability-13069055%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20of%20I