%20know%20English%20back%20then.%20But%20Brad%20and%20Lucy%20used%20sign%20language%20to%20ask%20us%20if%20they%20could%20live%20with%20us%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20We%20were%20surprised!%20Of%20course%20not!%E2%80%9D%20It%20was%20unheard%20of%20for%20foreigners%20to%20live%20with%20the%20villagers%20at%20the%20time.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20would%20we%20serve%20them%20to%20eat%3F%20Where%20would%20they%20sleep%3F%20All%20we%20could%20offer%20them%20was%20%3Cem%3Echarpais%20%3C%2Fem%3Eunder%20the%20open%20sky.%20We%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20compete%20with%20the%20luxuries%20of%20a%20hotel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Brad%20and%20Lucy%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ones%20to%20give%20up.%20The%20next%20morning%20they%20returned%20with%20a%20gentleman%20who%20was%20fluent%20in%20both%20English%20and%20Rajasthani%20dialect.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20communicated%20their%20request%20to%20us%20again%2C%20and%20told%20us%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20looking%20for%20luxuries%20but%20for%20an%20authentic%20Jodhpur%20experience%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290101%2Fbest-homestay-in-himachal-pradesh-sainj-valley-eco-friendly-kath-kuni-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20mud%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sleeping%20under%20the%20skies.%20Our%20home%20was%20perfect.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20the%20couple%20were%20welcomed%20into%20Pukhraj%20ji%E2%80%99s%20home%20for%20the%20next%2015%20days.%20And%2C%20unknown%20to%20Chhotaram%2C%20this%20would%20set%20the%20precedent%20for%20his%20dream%20homestay%20business%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-13-at-6.23.19-AM-1707396443.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chhotaram%20Prajapat%20Homestay%20in%20Salawas%