ototypes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20cutting%20the%20jeans%20in%20different%20sizes%20and%20lengths%20to%20understand%20what%20would%20work.%20We%20took%20help%20from%20our%20tailors%20to%20sew%20it.%20The%20first%20one%20was%20a%20little%20small.%20Every%20time%20we%20created%20a%20prototype%2C%20we%20compared%20it%20to%20the%20sleeping%20bag%20we%20had%20at%20home%20to%20achieve%20a%20similar%20level%20of%20comfort%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20his%20mother%2C%20Shivani%20Somany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20prototypes%20and%20one%20month%20later%2C%20the%20mother-son%20duo%20had%20cracked%20the%20code%20to%20stitch%20a%20perfect%20denim%20sleeping%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ftbi-donate-warmth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonate%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ftbi-donate-warmth%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fnirvaan4-min-1707372449.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nirvaan%20started%20Project%20Jeans%20in%202022%20to%20provide%20warmth%20to%20the%20homeless%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fnirvaan4-min-1707372449.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fnirvaan4-min-1707372449-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fnirvaan4-min-1707372449-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fnirvaan4-min-1707372449-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fnirvaan4-min-1707372449-1152x1536.jpg%201152w%2