20science%2C%20technology%2C%20engineering%2C%20and%20mathematics%20(STEM)%20interest%20among%20school%20children.%20By%20reaching%20out%20to%20schools%20that%20lack%20access%20to%20STEM%20labs%2C%20children%20in%20remote%20corners%20of%20the%20country%20are%20now%20able%20to%20enhance%20their%20scientific%20knowledge%2C%20grasp%20essential%20concepts%2C%20and%20develop%20problem-solving%20skills%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20school%20teachers%2C%20the%20remarkable%20outcome%20of%20this%20initiative%20is%20that%20even%20children%20who%20typically%20struggled%20in%20exams%20are%20now%20able%20to%20unleash%20their%20creativity%20and%20understand%20science%20concepts%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20traditional%20teaching%20methods%20often%20fall%20short%20of%20achieving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20winners%20%E2%80%94%20Joshwa%20A%20and%20Sivakarthikeyan%20N%20from%20Class%208%20at%20Government%20High%20School%2C%20Gerugambakkam%2C%20Chennai%20%E2%80%94%20ingeniously%20crafted%20the%20agricultural%20tricycle%20by%20repurposing%20an%20old%20cycle%2C%20scrap%20metal%2C%20and%20wheels%20acquired%20from%20a%20local%20scrap%20shop.%20Their%20teacher%2C%20Thenmughil%20Ramakrishnan%2C%20was%20initially%20surprised%20to%20see%20the%20boys%20transporting%20scrap%20materials%20to%20their%20homes%20daily.%20It%20was%20only%20later%20that%20she%20discovered%20they%20were%20constructing%20a%20device%20to%20assist%20farmers%20in%20performing%20multiple%20tasks%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20boys%20were%20in%20Class%206%20when%20the%20pandemic%20started.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20L%26amp%3BT%20started%20providing%20online%20classes%20to%20teach%20science%2C%20arts%20and%20maths.%20The%20students%20were%20given%20easy%20ways%20to%20make%20simple%20projects%20at%20home%2C%20which%20kept%20them%20occupied%20while%20they%20learnt%20the%20important%20concepts%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thenmughil%20tells%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20despite%20facing%20challenges%20in%20writing%20Tamil%20or%20English%20proficiently%2C%20these%20boys%20exhibit%20a%20remarkable%20understanding%20of%20science%20concepts.%20They%20independently%20constructed%20the%20entire%20device%2C%20delving%20into%20areas%20of%20agriculture%2C%20engineering%2C%20and%20beyond%20%E2%80%94%20showcasing%20their%20adeptness%20in%20practical%20knowledge%20and%20hands-on%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2024%20teams%20(50%20children)%20from%20Chennai%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20Hazira%2C%20Vadodara%2C%20Talegaon%20and%20Mumbai%20made%20it%20to%20the%20finals%2C%20which%20was%20conducted%20in%20Mumbai%20on%203%20February%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20STEM%20activities%20around%20existing%20curriculums%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201500px)%20100vw%2C%201500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22By%20connecting%20with%20underserved%20schools%20without%20STEM%20labs%2C%20children%20in%20remote%20areas%20can%20now%20improve%20their%20scientific%20knowledge.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935.jpeg%201500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340837%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBy%20connecting%20with%20underserved%20schools%20without%20STEM%20labs%2C%20children%20in%20remote%20areas%20can%20now%20improve%20their%20scientific%20knowledge.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility%20(CSR)%20initiatives%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20has%20been%20actively%20involved%20in%20the%20education%20sector%20for%20over%20three%20decades.%20Recognising%20that%20nearly%2080%20percent%20of%20future%20jobs%20will%20require%20science%20and%20math%20skills%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20aims%20to%20address%20the%20challenge%20of%20limited%20access%20and%20resources%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMabel%20Abraham%2C%20Head%20%E2%80%93%20Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility%20at%20L%26amp%3BT%2C%20explained%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20focus%20on%20STEM%20was%20made%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EL%26amp%3BT%20has%20undertaken%20a%20comprehensive%20approach%20to%20facilitate%20access%20to%20STEM%20education%20in%20government%20schools%20and%20schools%20with%20limited%20resources.%20This%20initiative%20is%20designed%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20and%20ensure%20that%20students%20have%20the%20necessary%20tools%20and%20opportunities%20to%20develop%20skills%20essential%20for%20the%20evolving%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20different%20models%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20STEM%20education%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302015%2Fboson-whitewater-bengaluru-startup-converts-stp-water-to-high-quality-potable-drinking-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20science%20labs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20implementing%20digital%20classrooms%2C%20and%20providing%20DIY%20kits%2C%20among%20other%20approaches.%20We%20did%20not%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20just%20one%20model%2C%20and%20instead%2C%20we%20decided%20on%20a%20blended%20