dia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen1-1706874295-500x270.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen1-1706874295-768x415.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen1-1706874295-150x81.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340621%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22654%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWomen%20packing%20Open%20Secret%20products%20at%20their%20factory%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20worked%20at%20Procter%20%26amp%3B%20Gamble%20(P%26amp%3BG)%20and%20General%20Mills%2C%20Ahana%20gained%20knowledge%20across%20various%20aspects%20of%20the%20consumer%20goods%20industry%2C%20spanning%20supply%20chain%2C%20finance%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20manufacturing.%20In%202019%2C%20she%20left%20General%20Mills%20and%20founded%20Open%20Secret.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20mother%2C%20the%20second%20director%2C%20provided%20the%20company%20with%20a%20paid-up%20capital%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh.%20Following%20the%20company%20registration%2C%20Ahana%20dedicated%20the%20next%20nine%20months%20to%20crafting%20the%20ideal%20%E2%80%98unjunked%E2%80%99%20snack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20securing%20investment%2C%20her%20initial%20priority%20was%20finding%20a%20suitable%20manufacturing%20facility.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20sure%20I%20wanted%20the%20shopfloor%20to%20be%20run%20by%20women.%20When%20I%20looked%20at%20manufacturing%20units%20in%20Bhiwandi%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20there%20was%20a%20big%20problem%20%E2%80%94%20there%20were%20no%20toilets%20for%20women%20as%20there%20were%20only%20men%20in%20all%20these%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20After%20many%20visits%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20set%20up%20her%20own%20factory%20in%20Bhandup%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20which%20would%20be%20operated%20by%20an%20all-women%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20and%20biggest%20challenge%20was%2C%20cracking%20the%20perfect%20recipe%20and%20setting%20up%20an%20assembly%20line%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tackle%20the%20first%20challenge%2C%20Ahana%20revisited%20her%20past%20experiences%20at%20other%20companies.%20During%20her%20time%20launching%20new%20products%20for%20a%20previous%20brand%2C%20she%20extensively%20visited%20customers%20in%20metro%20cities%2C%20gaining%20valuable%20insights%20into%20their%20snacking%20preferences.%20Drawing%20on%20this%20knowledge%2C%20she%20conducted%20focus%20groups%20to%20identify%20customer%20favourites%20in%20snacks%2C%20cookies%2C%20biscuits%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20focus%20groups%2C%20we%20asked%20people%20what%20they%20liked%20and%20disliked%20in%20the%20snacks%20they%20were%20eating.%20The%20uniform%20response%20from%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20working%20professionals%2C%20students%20or%20moms%20%E2%80%94%20was%20the%20maida.%20I%20then%20asked%20them%20what%20they%20found%20healthy%2C%20to%20which%20most%20said%20dry%20fruits%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20this%20feedback%20and%20with%20the%20help%20of%20an%20in-house%20R%26amp%3BD%20team%2C%20Ahana%20worked%20on%20formulating%20the%20perfect%20%E2%80%98unjunked%E2%80%99%20cookie.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20unjunked%20the%20typical%20cookie%20by%20replacing%20maida%20with%2040%20to%2050%20percent%20dry%20fruits%20and%20millet%20using%20less%20sugar.%20Most%20of%20our%20products%20have%20just%201%20to%202%20grams%20of%20sugar%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20involved%20a%20group%20of%20100%20mothers%2C%20dubbed%20by%20Ahana%20as%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Chief%20Innovation%20Officers%E2%80%99.%20Ahana%20sent%20them%20various%20flavours%20and%20samples%2C%20using%20their%20feedback%20to%20improve%20the%20products.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20helped%20us%20crack%20the%20right%20product%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ahana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20asserts%20that%20they%20have%20taken%20measures%20to%20guarantee%20the%20snacks%20remain%20delectable%20even%20after%20substituting%20certain%20ingredients%20with%20their%20nutritious%20counterparts.%20This%20ensures%20that%20customers%20not%20only%20enjoy%20the%20taste%20but%20also%20reap%20health%20benefits%20from%20their%20consumption.%20Hence%2C%20nine%20months%20and%201%2C000%20cookies%20later%2C%20Ahana%20was%20ready%20with%20the%20first%20product%20%E2%80%94%20the%20nutty%20cookie%2C%20which%20to%20date%20is%20their%20bestseller.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20challenge%20was%20learning%20how%20to%20manufacture%20the%20product.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20one-of-a-kind%20product%20with%20no%20benchmark.%20I%20had%20to%20use%20my%20engineering%20skills%20to%20set%20up%20the%20right%20assembly%20line.%20We%20also%20had%20to%20work%20on%20extending%20the%20shelf%20life%20without%20adding%20preservatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20uses%20aluminium%20in%20the%20packaging%20to%20extend%20the%20shelf%20life%20of%20her%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhana%20finally%20launched%20%E2%80%98Open%20Secret%E2%80%99%20in%20January%202020%20through%20online%20and%20offline%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Open%20Secret%20has%20over%2030%20categories%20of%20products%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981.jpeg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340793%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20does%20a%20new%20brand%20draw%20in%20customers%20and%20persuade%20them%20to%20purchase%3F%20Ahana%20applied%20her%20MBA%20knowledge%2C%20utilising%20the%20concept%20of%20shopper%20marketing%20to%20promote%20Open%20Secret.%20She%20and%20her%20team%20visited%20stores%2C%20providing%20free%20samples%20of%20their%20products.%20According%20to%20the%20CEO%2C%20everyone%20who%20tried%20the%20product%20ended%20up%20making%20a%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20made%20Open%20Secret%20visible%20at%20the%20point%20of%20purchase%20in%20supermarkets%20and%20stores.%20We%20did%20many%20free%20trials%20of%20the%20product%2C%20as%20once%20they%20try%2C%20they%20will%20buy.%20We%20also%20incentivised%20customers%20using%20discounts%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ahana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20mentions%20that%20they%20also%20employed%20blind%20tasting%20to%20assess%20their%20products%20with%20consumers.%20According%20to%20Ahana%2C%20their%20Unique%20Selling%20Proposition%20(USP)%20lies%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20their%20product%20replicates%20the%20taste%20of%20junk%20food%2C%20fulfilling%20people%E2%80%99s%20cravings%20healthily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20slowly%20started%20building%20their%20presence%2C%20they%20faced%20their%20first%20roadblock%20two%20months%20later%20as%20COVID-19%20hit%20India.%20Not%20one%20to%20bow%20down%20during%20a%20crisis%2C%20Ahana%20worked%20on%20converting%20it%20into%20an%20opportunity.%20They%20focused%20on%20online%20channels%20and%20were%20able%20to%20operate%20during%20the%20lockdown%20as%20they%20fell%20under%20the%20essential%20categories%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20hustled%20through%20COVID-19.%20Once%2C%20the%20cooling%20refrigeration%20system%20at%20the%20factory%20stopped%20working%20during%20the%20lockdown.%20We%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20any%20technician%20but%20needed%20a%20refrigerator%20to%20store%20our%20chocolates%20and%20products.%20I%20brought%20my%20refrigerator%20from%20home%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20we%20averted%20a%20major%20crisis%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20Ahana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20themselves%20visible%20online%2C%20they%20used%20banners%20and%20discounts%2C%20and%20placed%20their%20products%20across%20online%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founder%20states%20that%20they%20grew%20multi-fold%20amid%20the%20pandemic%20and%20sold%20over%2010%20lakh%20cookies.%20Since%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20Open%20Secret%20sells%20over%2030%20products%2C%20including%20cookies%2C%20biscuits%2C%20chips%2C%20dry%20fruits%2C%20snacks%2C%20chocolates%2C%20brownies%2C%20cereals%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20present%20across%20online%20channels%20including%20Amazon%2C%20Flipkart%2C%20their%20own%20website%2C%20and%20quick%20commerce%20chains%20like%20Zepto%2C%20Blinkit%2C%20Big%20Basket%20and%20more.%20They%20also%20sell%20through%20supermarkets%20offline.%20Through%20their%20platform%2C%20they%20also%20partner%20with%20and%20sell%20products%20from%20over%20100%20healthy%20brands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhana%20states%20that%20they%20will%20achieve%20gross%20sales%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore%20this%20year%20and%20wants%20to%20become%20a%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20company%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98An%20ode%20to%20my%20mother%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201083px)%20100vw%2C%201083px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221083%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ahana%20studied%20at%20Harvard%20Business%20School%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286.jpeg%201083w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286-227x300.jpeg%20227w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286-500x660.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286-768x1014.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286-150x198.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340618%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221430%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAhana%20studied%20at%20Harvard%20Business%20School.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpen%20Secret%E2%80%99s%20USP%2C%20besides%20its%20snacks%2C%20is%20its%20women%2C%20says%20Ahana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20factories%20are%20run%20by%20200%20women%20and%20over%2050%20percent%20of%20its%20employees%20are%20women.%20Why%3F%20Ahana%20believes%20that%20women%20leaders%20like%20her%2C%20who%20are%20privileged%2C%20must%20provide%20opportunities%20to%20women.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20was%20due%20to%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20belief%20that%20this%20girl%20from%20Bharatpur%20went%20to%20IIT%2C%20and%20Harvard%2C%20and%20launched%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290986%2Fhemapriya-natesan-sathumaavu-traditional-powder-for-babies-no-sugar-startup-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eown%20brand.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20still%20treat%20a%20single%20woman%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20judgement.%20When%20I%20returned%20to%20India%2C%20everyone%20assumed%20that%20it%20was%20either%20because%20of%20visa%20issues%20or%20marriage.%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20a%20single%20woman%20follow%20her%20passions%3F%20Why%20is%20getting%20married%20the%20only%20way%20to%20settle%20down%3F%E2%80%9D%20asks%20Ahana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20for%20women%20is%20to%20have%20a%20good%20education%20and%20be%20financially%20independent.%20%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99ll%20be%20unstoppable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20lucky%20because%20my%20mother%20gave%20me%20that%20opportunity%2C%20but%20not%20everyone%20gets%20it.%20Women%20leaders%20have%20the%20responsibility%20to%20provide%20jobs%20to%20other%20women.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20create%20an%20equal%20world%20for%20young%20girls.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpen%20Secret%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20is%20Ahana%E2%80%99s%20love%20letter%20to%20her%20single%20mother%2C%20who%20showed%20her%20daughter%20that%20nothing%20is%20impossible.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20an%20%E2%80%98open%20secret%E2%80%99%20that%20we%20are%20who%20we%20are%20because%20of%20our%20mothers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20proud%20daughter%20dedicating%20her%20brand%20to%20all%20mothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ahana%E2%80%99s%20mother%20saw%20her%20daughter%20open%20her%20wings%20and%20fly%2C%20she%20passed%20away%20during%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20COVID-19%20in%202021.%20Ahana%20had%20to%20make%20a%20tough%20choice%20the%20next%20day%20as%20she%20had%20an%20investor%20meeting%20to%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20either%20pause%20and%20grieve%2C%20or%20pitch%20to%20the%20investor%20for%20our%20Series%20A%20round%2C%20and%20I%20chose%20the%20latter%2C%20as%20I%20had%20to%20build%20this%20brand%20and%20keep%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20alive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707134492000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp